Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,睡梦医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪  薇奥莱特[意为紫罗兰]\NWhere you going, Violet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去采些花儿\NJust to pick some flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别走远了\NDon't wander too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,佛罗里达州\N1980年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,? 我的爱尔兰野玫瑰 ?\N? My wild Irish rose ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,? 是最甜美的花朵 ?\N? The sweetest flower that grows ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,? 任你遍寻世间 ?\N? You may search everywhere ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,? 也没什么能和我的爱尔兰野玫瑰媲美 ?\N? But none can compare with my wild Irish rose ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\NWell, hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在哪找到那些的\NWhere did you find those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道所有的秘密地点\NI know all the secret places.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要一朵吗\NDo you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想我为何戴着这顶可笑的帽子\NYou're wondering why I'm wearing such a funny hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直戴着它\NI always wear this hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,经常戴  它都成我名字的一部分了\NSo much, it's a part of my name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友们...\NMy friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,非常非常好的朋友  他们喊我帽子萝西\Nmy very, very best friends, they just call me Rose the Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看着象是魔法师的帽子\NIt looks like a magician's hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是顶魔法帽子\NIt's a magic hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看看吗\NDo you wanna see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我手上没东西\NNothing up my sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,帽子里也没东西\NNothing in my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别害怕  那是我朋友\NDon't worry, that's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你要错过戏法了\NYou're missing the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把手伸进去\NReach inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-太漂亮了  -因为它很特别\N- It's so pretty. - Because it's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,说到特别\NAnd speaking of special,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是个小魔法师  是不是\Nyou're a little magic, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我手里的花  是什么颜色的\NThe flower in my hand, what color is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  宝贝\NOh, it's okay, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会被吓到的  我保证\NYou won't scare me. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,紫色的\NPurple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,紫罗兰\NViolet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一样\Nlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,花不能吃的\NYou don't eat flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吃\NBut you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些花很特别\NBut these are special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝  特别的才最好吃\NHoney, it's the special ones that taste best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我该回去找我妈妈了\NI should get back to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别走  再待一会儿\NNo, stay. Stay awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,多看点魔术\NSee more magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个特别的小东西  是不是\NYou are a special little thing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,薇奥莱特\NViolet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,薇奥莱特\NViolet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,薇奥莱特\NViolet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,薇...\NVi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,第一章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,旧日的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了  医生\NHey. It's okay, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,干干爽爽\NAll dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你得和我说话啊  丹尼\NYou have to talk to me, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来后一直没说话  自从...\NYou haven't talked since we left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  医生\NPlease, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不说话是吧  医生\Nyou ain't talking, huh, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次见你时你也不怎么说话\NWeren't talking much first time I met you neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小男孩一个\NLittle boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不在那个可怕的地方度过漫长的冬天\Nset to spend a long winter at that rotten old place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有他和他爸爸妈妈\NJust him and his mommy and daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸有多黑暗  小男孩就有多光明\NDaddy as dark as that boy is bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小男孩可明亮了\NAnd, boy, is he bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的闪灵像团火一样发着光\NHe's shining like fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,然而那个地方\Nin the one place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对于有闪灵能力的人而言是最不好的\Nthe worst place for someone who shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得我们第一次真正的交流吗\NYou remember the first time we really talked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你脑子里说话的那次\NWhen I spoke up inside your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那次让你感觉很好  是吧\NMade you feel good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,得知自己并不孤独\NKnowing you weren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸想杀了我\NDaddy tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他那时已经不是他了  你得理解\NIt wasn't all him, you gotta know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个地方供养了他的黑暗  蚕食了你的光明\NThat place fed his dark, like it fed on your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他内心也是有光明的\NAnd he had some light in him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就和你内心也是有黑暗的一样\NJust like you got some dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是既光明又黑暗\NWe all got both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,它还没有放过我\NIt's not done with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有想过我每次都是怎样出现的\NIt ever strike you funny how I showed up when I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,每当你需要我的时候\NWhen you needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有人也这样帮助过我\NSomeone did that for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我奶奶教我的\NMy grandma taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而我教给了你\Nand I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有朝一日  丹尼·托伦斯\NAnd some day, Danny Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会教给别人\Nyou'll teach someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:10:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会的\NI won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会是吗\NOh, you won't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说我不会再用闪灵了\NI won't shine, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不会了  太危险了\NNo more. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜有时候是的\NReckon it is sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她找到我了\NShe found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她会不断来找我  直到她抓到我\NShe'll come back and come back until she gets me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,眺望酒店已经荒废了  被封起来了\NThe Overlook's condemned. Boarded up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那些饥饿的老鬼魂\NThey're starvin' old ghosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在到处找你\Nand they're reachin' out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不会只有她一个的\NWon't stop with her, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,书里的插画\NPictures in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过他们只是书里的插画\NYou said they were just pictures in a book
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们伤害不了我\Nand they couldn't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对于一些东西而言\NSome things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一些黑暗的东西  闪灵如同食物\Ndark things, the shining's like food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是闻到腥味的苍蝇\NThey're mosquitoes landing for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,眺望酒店\NThe Overlook,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我而言它向来都只是插画\Nit was always just pictures to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的闪灵能力没你强\NBut I didn't shine like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人的闪灵能力有你强\NNobody shines like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你在那个破酒店里\NSo, you in that damn hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就象是个百万伏的电池\Nyou was like a million-watt battery all plugged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,酒店被充了电\NAnd it ate it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你让它变成了真的\NYou made it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你踏进酒店门的那一刻就开始了\NStarted soon as you walked through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对此无能为力  很抱歉告诉你这点\NCan't do nothing about that, I'm sorry to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但你已经不是小孩子了\Nbut you're not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经长大了\NYou're older now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,从某种程度上讲  成熟了不少\NMuch older, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须听好了\NYou gotta hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个饥肠辘辘的世界\NWorld's a hungry place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,最黑暗的东西也是最饥饿的\NAnd the darkest things are the hungriest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会蚕食一切发光的东西\Nand they'll eat what shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就像蚊子蚂蝗一样成群结队\NSwarm it like mosquitoes or leeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人们对此无能为力\NCan't do nothing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而你能做的\NWhat you can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是用他们渴求的东西来对付他们\Nis turn what they come for against 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我爷爷\NMy grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个刻薄的老混蛋\Nhe was a mean son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,内心很黑暗\NDark inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和你爸爸一样的黑暗\NSame type of dark as your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾把我和我奶奶打到不省人事\NBeat me senseless, and my grandma, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他死的时候  我开心得手舞足蹈\Nand when he died, I danced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不断地回来\NBut he kept on coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,站在我房间里\NStanding in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,穿得灰不溜秋的\NSuit all gray
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,浑身都是棺材里他身上长的霉散发的恶臭\Nand stinkin' from whatever mold was growin' on him in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天  他抓住了我  他成了真的\NOne day, he grabbed me, and he was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他的指甲很长\NHis nails were long
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是在坟墓里长的\Nfrom growing in the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他抓伤了我  医生\Nand they cut me, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很深的口子\NCut me deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我奶奶\NSo, Grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她教了我一个办法\Nshe taught me a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,给了我一个礼物\NGave me a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你好好熟悉这个盒子\NI want you to know this box...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,里里外外\Ninside and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别光是看  摸摸它\NDon't just look at it. Touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把鼻子探进去  闻闻有没有味道\NStick your nose inside and see if there's a smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,熟悉每一个角落\NKnow every corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每一个细节\Nevery single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
