Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.47,0:29:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别想睡午觉了\NWe can forget about naptime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.27,0:29:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再坚持几小时就好\NJust a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.36,0:29:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我说  "再坚持几小时就好"\NSay it with me. "Just a few more hours."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.03,0:29:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再坚持几小时就好\NJust a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.07,0:29:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么鬼\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.38,0:29:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\NDave...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.77,0:30:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妈咪妈咪哄\NAbracadabra.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,第二章
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.17,0:30:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,空洞的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.31,0:30:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  瞌睡虫\NWell, hi there, sleepyhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.39,0:30:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不让你睡沉一点\NI had to sleep you pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.57,0:30:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你很难搞定\NYou're a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.53,0:30:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,意志很强\NWillful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.03,0:31:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  我查了\NYou know, I checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.86,0:31:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,三个月里有六个男人\NSix men in three months
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.45,0:31:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,脸上被文了那种蛇咬文身\Nwith those little snakebite tattoos on their cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.78,0:31:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真忙啊\NWhy, you've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.96,0:31:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,蛇咬安蒂  原来就是你\NSnakebite Andi, that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.05,0:31:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我是谁\NSo, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.68,0:31:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是绑架了我的疯婆子\NYou're some crazy bitch who kidnapped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.72,0:31:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始只说实话\NJust the truth from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.43,0:31:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你将只说实话\NYou will only speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.23,0:31:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我见过的最美的女人\NYou're the most beautiful woman I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.36,0:31:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,天  效果也太好了点  是吧\NMy God. Works a little too well, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.44,0:31:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了  蛇咬安蒂\NHere's the deal, Snakebite Andi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.49,0:31:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个说服者  对吧  你可以说服人们\NYou're a pusher, hmm? You can push people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一阵子没有说服者了\NWe haven't had a pusher around here for a little while,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.49,0:31:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要给你开一个条件\Nso I'm gonna offer you a deal
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这条件我快四十年没给人开过了\NI haven't offered anyone in almost 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你多大了  亲爱的\NHow old are you, darlin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.50,0:32:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,十五岁\NFifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,十五岁\NFifteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.05,0:32:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,天  多好的年纪啊\NOh, God, what an age.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.09,0:32:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,正是含苞待放的时候  是吧\NSpringtime of your womanhood, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.64,0:32:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经不是小女孩了\NYou're not a girl anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.14,0:32:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也还没有一点岁月的痕迹\Nbut you don't have a single dent yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.06,0:32:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,地心引力甚至都没注意到你\NGravity hasn't even noticed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.11,0:32:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,十五岁的时候不会\NNot at 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.23,0:32:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不过男人嘛\NMen, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.99,0:32:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  不用害羞\NNo, no, no. No shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.99,0:32:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你通通还回去了  对吧\NYou paid that back, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我要提供给你的  青春永驻\NThat's what I'm offering you. Springtime forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.04,0:32:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起十年后  你还是十五岁\NTen years from now, you're still 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.33,0:32:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一百年后  可能十七岁\NA hundred, maybe 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.59,0:32:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,吃得好\NEat well,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.96,0:32:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,永葆青春  长生不老\Nstay young, live long.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.26,0:32:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你和你朋友...\NSo, you and your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的朋友  那是我的家人\NNot my friend. That's my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.98,0:32:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是真结族  亲爱的\NWe're the True Knot, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.56,0:33:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真结族\NThe True Knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.69,0:33:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,绑定之物无法解绑\NWhat's tied can never be untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.51,0:33:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,新罕布什尔州  弗雷泽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.12,0:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,城市药房  肥皂盒专卖店
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.69,0:34:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗\NYou like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.81,0:34:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我只是...\NSorry. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.94,0:34:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  人们总喜欢凑近了看\NThat's okay. People love to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.19,0:34:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以前都是在图书馆里布置这些的\NWe used to set this up in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.40,0:34:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,社区项目  仿佛自己活过来了\NCommunity project, just taking a life all its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看  我们是从那边的钟楼开始的\NSee, we started with the clock tower there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.91,0:34:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗  -越建越多\N- Oh, yeah. - Just keeps growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.24,0:34:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们叫它迷你镇\NKids call it Teenytown.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.75,0:34:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是孩子们建的\NThe kids build this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.21,0:34:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在一些帮助之下  是的\NWith some help, oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.92,0:34:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,继续下去就能建好整个城镇广场\NKeep it up, build the whole town square.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.59,0:34:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是坐大巴来的还是搭的顺风车\NAre you off the bus or riding your thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.76,0:34:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大巴\NYeah, the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.84,0:34:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很少有人会坐大巴来这么北部的地方\NNot many ride the bus this far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.80,0:34:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,除非是想找工作\NUnless they're looking for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.23,0:35:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是想换个环境\NChange of scenery,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.90,0:35:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在逃离什么\Nor you running away from something?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.94,0:35:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意  希望我没有...\NDon't mind me. I hope I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.64,0:35:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想跟新面孔聊聊\NNew face is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.81,0:35:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.31,0:35:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我是在逃离自己吧\NGuess I'm running away from myself, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.03,0:35:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.28,0:35:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识这种表情  恐怕是太熟悉了\NI know that look. Too well, I'm sorry to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.66,0:35:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,逃离自己  这可不好办\NRunning away from yourself. That is a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.08,0:35:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不管去哪都得带着自己\NYou take yourself with you wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.33,0:35:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很操蛋吧\NAin't that the bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.17,0:35:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,租金85一周\NRent's 85 a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.50,0:35:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要先付钱\Npayable up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.96,0:35:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比利帮你付了头两周的钱  其余的你得自己交\NBilly paid your first two, rest's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.51,0:35:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不能养宠物  不能办派对  不能吵闹\NNo pets, no parties, no noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.14,0:35:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个安静的租客\NI'm a quiet tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上一个人也是这么说的  学数学的学生\NLast guy said the same. Math student.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.06,0:35:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至让他把墙刷成了黑板\NEven let him paint the wall all blackboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.06,0:35:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好让他在上面演算他的谜题\Nso he could scribble his little puzzles up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.02,0:36:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不安静  一点都不\NWasn't quiet. No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.86,0:36:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走的时候都没给我刷回原样  不过幸好没刷\NDidn't even paint over this when he left, but I'm glad he didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能让你轻松记住了\N'cause I can make this easy for ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.70,0:36:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你每天醒来都会看到它\Nso you see it every morning when you wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.12,0:36:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,85一周\N老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.25,0:36:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要帮这小子做担保吗\NYou sure you wanna vouch for this pup?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.83,0:36:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,非常确定\NPretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.42,0:36:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,倒霉的是你  比利\NIt's your ass, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙就是心太软\NBleedin' heart, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.30,0:36:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我在楼下  一楼  有需要可以找我\NI'm downstairs, ground floor, if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.84,0:36:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明天来找我  聊聊工作的事\NFind me tomorrow, talk about some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.93,0:36:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要做这些\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.14,0:36:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不认识我\NYou don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.64,0:36:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NNo, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.48,0:36:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认识你那表情  我之前说过了\NBut I know the look, like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.36,0:36:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我对人会有种第六感\NAnd sometimes I get this feeling about people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.90,0:36:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可能很难理解\NHard to understand, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.95,0:36:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没你想的那么难\NEasier than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.16,0:36:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢了  -没事\N- Thanks. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.26,0:37:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\NYou ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.06,0:37:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她准备好了\NShe's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.36,0:37:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人是谁\NWho... Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你一会就知道了\NYou'll find out after.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.65,0:37:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那个是弗力克大爷\NThat over there is Grampa Flick...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.57,0:37:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他会引导我们  躺下\Nand he'll lead us. Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.33,0:37:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕  明白吗\NNo fear. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.01,0:37:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是真结族\NWe are the True Knot
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.47,0:37:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们生生不息\Nand we endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.02,0:37:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是天选之子\NWe are the chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.19,0:38:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是幸运之人\NWe are the fortunate ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.94,0:38:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,绑定之物无法解绑\NWhat is tied cannot be untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.20,0:38:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一个女人\NHere is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她会加入我们吗\NWould she join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.41,0:38:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她会把自己的命与我们绑定吗\NWould she tie her life to our life?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.75,0:38:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.17,0:38:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,说是的\NSay yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.55,0:38:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.51,0:38:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很特别\NThis one's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.35,0:38:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫维奥莱特\NHer name's Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.14,0:38:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经所剩无几了\NThere's not much of her left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.19,0:38:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而她的味道\NAnd she tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.77,0:38:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如同花朵\Nlike flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.13,0:39:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,深吸气\NBreathe deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.18,0:39:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对  接受它\NThere. Embrace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.69,0:39:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,接受它\NEmbrace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.00,0:39:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.66,0:39:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.64,0:40:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还没找到我们\NThey haven't found us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.77,0:40:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们听惯了他的哭声\NThey were used to hearing him cry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.39,0:40:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我总是扔下他一个人\N'cause I left him alone so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.48,0:40:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们无动于衷\NSo they didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.65,0:40:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还没发现我们\NAnd they haven't found us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.83,0:41:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.36,0:41:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你认识我的表情\NUh, you said that you knew my look.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.99,0:41:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么意思\NWell, what did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.11,0:41:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟\NBrother...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.41,0:41:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你病了\Nyou're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你很累  我看得出来\NYou're tired. I can see that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.58,0:41:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你又十分厌倦这种状态\NBut you're sick and tired of being sick and tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.17,0:41:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要帮助\NI need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.05,0:41:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\NCome on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.51,0:42:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊聊\NWe'll talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.14,0:42:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝  请赐予我平静的心去接受我无法改变的\NGod, grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.65,0:42:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,赐予我勇气去改变我能改变的事情\Nthe courage to change the things I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.27,0:42:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,赐予我智慧去分辨两者\Nand the wisdom to know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.15,0:42:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,博比今天过生日\NWell, Bobbie's got a big birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.24,0:42:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,三年整  戒酒三年\NThree years. Three years sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.61,0:42:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,棒\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.66,0:42:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我太为你骄傲了\NI'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.49,0:42:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  约翰\NThanks, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.33,0:42:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记谁了吗\NNow, am I forgetting anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.38,0:42:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有一年整的  或者半年的\NDoes anybody got a year? Or six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.50,0:42:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到屋子里最重要的人了\NWell, now for the most important person in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.22,0:42:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有新来的吗\NIs, uh, anybody here a newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.97,0:42:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有人戒酒24小时了吗\NSomebody got 24 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.89,0:42:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.82,0:42:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,新搬来的\NNew to town, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.44,0:42:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我...\NYeah, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.49,0:43:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没别的意思  这屋子里有一半人是我接生的\NNothing personal. I delivered half the people in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.20,0:43:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-只是看到了新面孔而已  -这位是丹·托伦斯\N- Just new faces pop, that's all. - This here is Dan Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.91,0:43:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,刚乘大巴来的\NHe's fresh off the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.91,0:43:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子也刚摔了一跤\NFresh off the ground, by the look.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.04,0:43:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不会评头论足  兄弟\NThere's no judgment here, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.75,0:43:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都经历过\NI mean, we've all been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-经历过更惨的  相信我  -是的\N- And worse, trust me. - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.59,0:43:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这位医生  我记事起他就在我们镇上工作\NDoc, he's served our town most my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.51,0:43:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-我弟弟就是他接生的  -是的\N- Delivered my baby brother. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.13,0:43:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基最近怎么样\NHow is Frankie these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.93,0:43:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他会迷途知返的\NWell, he'll find his way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.43,0:43:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他内心深处是个好人\NYou know, he's got a good heart under it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.22,0:43:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比利真的尽力帮他了  我们都尽力了\NBilly really tried with him. Well, we all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  要知道\NWell, Billy, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.77,0:43:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要一个可以避风的港湾\Nif you're looking for a wing to climb under...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.19,0:43:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对找不到比比利·弗里曼更靠谱的了\NI can't say you'll do any better than Billy Freeman here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.98,0:43:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的热情招待\NThank you for your hospitality. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.78,0:43:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点\NI'm a little, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.28,0:43:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能还是不习惯\NI guess I'm not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.20,0:43:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道有句话\NWell, you know we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.28,0:43:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"不了解来龙去脉  就不能妄加评判别人"\N"You can't judge someone till you know their whole story."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.58,0:43:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能觉得自己明白\NYou might think you understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.12,0:43:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-但其实不明白  -不明白\N- but you don't. - You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.04,0:43:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天过得怎么样  还好吗\NSo, how are you today? All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.33,0:43:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小火车还在开\NTrain's still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.92,0:43:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那挺好的\NThat's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.88,0:43:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou good?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  没事\NYeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.51,0:44:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  丹\NWell, good to know you, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.72,0:44:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-我也是  -有空再来\N- Yeah. - Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.97,0:44:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -希望很快能再见面\N- Thanks. - Hope to see you again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.14,0:44:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来的\NI'll... I'll come back, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.93,0:44:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,人特别好  他很有天赋\NReally good man. He's got a gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.60,0:44:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是  比利  等下\NYeah. Hey, Billy, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.44,0:44:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\NHey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.98,0:44:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手表\NYour watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.69,0:44:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手表丢了  你当时担心那个孩子  得了\NYou lost your watch. You were worried about the kid with, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.78,0:44:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,古雪氏\NGoocher's.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.36,0:44:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.12,0:44:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,得了古氏或者高氏的那个孩子  骨头的病\NThe kid with Goocher's or Gaucher's. The bone thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.62,0:44:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,高雪氏症\NGaucher's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.54,0:44:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.42,0:44:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你在医院的洗手间洗手\NYou were washing your hands in the hospital bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.21,0:44:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它放在洗手液旁边了\Nand you left it on the soap dispenser.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.51,0:44:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看洗手液旁边就行了\NJust check on the soap dispenser.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.05,0:44:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-很高兴认识你  -好\N- It's good to meet you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.31,0:44:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的\NHow did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.77,0:44:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰·道尔顿医生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.10,0:44:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望能说清楚\NI wish I could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.57,0:45:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,碰巧猜到的\NLucky guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.94,0:45:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,瞎说\NMy ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.57,0:45:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是直觉  直觉告诉我的\NIntuition, I suppose. Like a feeling in my gut. Maybe a...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.99,0:45:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,碰巧猜中了\NA lucky guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.16,0:45:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在这里做什么\NWhat do you wanna do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.42,0:45:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.46,0:45:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说在弗雷泽  你为什么来这里\NI mean here in Frazier. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.55,0:45:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我说套话  丹\NAnd don't bullshit me, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.67,0:45:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我更相信自己的直觉\NI'm prone to gut feelings of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.55,0:45:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我也说不好\NI don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.64,0:45:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,做些跟我以前做的不一样的事\NSomething different than I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.52,0:45:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好一点的事\NSomething better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.56,0:45:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说  做什么都比以前好\NAnything's better, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.77,0:45:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你做礼拜吗\NYou go to church?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.19,0:45:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,重要吗\NDoes it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.28,0:45:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有信仰吗  比你\NDo you believe in something? Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.49,0:45:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,更宏大的东西\Nbigger than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.70,0:45:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,信仰不能让我们成为更好的人\NOur... Our beliefs don't make us better people.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.33,0:45:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,行动才能让我们成为更好的人\NOur actions make us better people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.00,0:46:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,比利说  你有过做护工的经验\NSo, Billy says you have orderly experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.63,0:46:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.21,0:46:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在有工作吗\NYou workin' right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.76,0:46:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在迷你镇做零工 帮忙看小火车\NA few shifts at Teenytown. Helping with the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.51,0:46:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我每周在利文顿临终安养院工作三天\N'Cause I do three days a week at Rivington House, the hospice.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.14,0:46:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的护工很难找\NGood orderly is tough to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.97,0:46:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,留住更难\NTougher to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.64,0:46:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕垂死的人吗\NDo dying people bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.81,0:46:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.56,0:46:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会死\NWe're all dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.11,0:46:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界就是个空气清新的大型安养院\NThe world is one big hospice with fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.12,0:47:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\NWell, hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.33,0:47:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-我睡了多久...  -几天\N- How long was I... - Oh, few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.63,0:47:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说不会疼的\NYou said it didn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.51,0:47:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不疼了  对吧\NDoesn't now, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.38,0:47:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当时感觉我要死了\NFelt like I was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.35,0:47:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.89,0:47:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你确实死了\NYou did.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.73,0:47:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我复活了\NYou brought me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.02,0:47:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等你吃了东西就会好受些\NYou'll feel better when you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.19,0:47:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是人类吗\NAm I still human?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.07,0:47:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在乎吗\NDo you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.15,0:47:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,? It's all forgotten now ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.15,0:47:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's All Forgotten Now - Ray Noble and His Orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.70,0:47:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,? The trouble and the pain ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.32,0:47:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,? Forgotten, Every word I said ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.20,0:48:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,? Every tear you shed ?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.00,0:48:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,? We're still in love ?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.63,0:48:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.88,0:48:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.14,0:48:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕我\NYou're scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.27,0:48:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们爱你胜过世界上的一切\NWe love you more than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.27,0:48:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.73,0:48:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,胜过一切\NAnything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.70,0:48:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安  亲爱的\NGoodnight, my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.95,0:49:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别去烦他\NLet him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.33,0:49:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,阿兹里  别烦他\NAzreel, leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.30,0:49:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,阿兹\NAzzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.89,0:49:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阿兹  过来\NAzzie, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.31,0:49:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,过来  阿兹\NCome on. Azzie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.10,0:49:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\NDoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.23,0:49:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗  医生\NThat you, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.19,0:49:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不是医生\NNo, I'm not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.81,0:49:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我帮你叫医生过来吗\NDo you want me to get you a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.94,0:49:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,猫到我的床上来了\NThe cat's on my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.11,0:49:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它弄走\NI'll move her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.99,0:49:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.53,0:49:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道它会来\NI knew she would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.99,0:50:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这只猫似乎一直都知道\NThat cat always seems to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.87,0:50:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大限是什么时候\Nwhen it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.04,0:50:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-我猜大限到了  -不\N- I guess it's time. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.54,0:50:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿兹就是一只傻乎乎的猫\NIt's just Azzie being a silly old cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.25,0:50:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.42,0:50:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我来到这里就一直这样\NBeen that way ever since I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.09,0:50:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这只猫知道\NThe cat knows
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.18,0:50:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候该长睡不醒了\Nwhen it's time to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.56,0:50:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道\NEverybody knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.10,0:50:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要死了\NI'm gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.66,0:50:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.95,0:50:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你叫人来\NLet me get you someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.08,0:50:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.08,0:50:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道大限到了\NKnown it was comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.96,0:50:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不代表就不感到害怕了\NDoesn't make it less scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.38,0:50:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.80,0:50:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但也许就像你说的\NBut maybe it's just like you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.21,0:50:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只是睡过去了\Njust going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.05,0:51:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的  只是睡着了\NI mean, there's nothing scary. It's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.35,0:51:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是奇怪的医生\NYou're a strange type of doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.06,0:51:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-我说过了  我不是医生  -我觉得你是\N- I told you, I'm not a doctor. - Oh, I think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.52,0:51:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,睡梦医生\NDoctor Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.69,0:51:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,医生  我怕会疼  会很黑\NDoc, I am so scared it's gonna hurt, or be dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.40,0:51:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,或者会化为虚无  我不想...\Nor... or be nothing at all. And I don't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.57,0:51:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的\NNothing to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.16,0:51:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只是睡着而已\NJust going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.12,0:51:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,终于能真正安宁地睡着\NFinally, true, restful sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.88,0:51:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NOh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.67,0:51:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  医生\NThank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.05,0:51:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该在这里  我去帮你叫...\NLook, I shouldn't be here. Let me go get you some...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.47,0:51:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不用\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.22,0:51:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你恰恰应该在这里\NYou're exactly where you should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.14,0:51:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.23,0:51:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见我的妻子了\NI see my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.32,0:52:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.09,0:53:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.77,0:54:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,第三章
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.54,0:54:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.42,0:54:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是丹  我酗酒\NDan, alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.05,0:54:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,八年后
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.55,0:54:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  丹\NHi, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.01,0:54:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是一个善于言辞的人\NI'm not much of a speech guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.55,0:54:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我应该握着这个纪念章\NI just thought I'd hold the chip and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.47,0:54:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想到什么说什么\Ntalk about whatever popped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.56,0:54:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我站在了这里\NSo, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.98,0:54:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到了我爸\NAnd I'm thinkin' about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.32,0:54:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一次见过他手里拿着这样的纪念章\NI saw a chip like this in his hand once.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.40,0:54:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就在他去世前的几个月\NA couple months before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.41,0:54:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,五个月纪念章  我很确定\NFive month chip, I'm pretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.00,0:54:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次他喝醉后伤害了我\NHe hurt me once when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.58,0:55:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,弄断了我的胳膊\NBroke my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.92,0:55:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他就戒酒了\NThen he dried right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.01,0:55:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我五岁时他去世了  所以我了解他的唯一方式\NHe died when I was five, so the only way I got to know him,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.59,0:55:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真正了解他的方式  就在我堕落的时候\Nreally got to know him, was when I went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.89,0:55:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝得天昏地暗的时候\NWhen I... When I drank to dull the...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.44,0:55:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或者\Nor, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.65,0:55:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要暴打别人的时候\Nwhenever I wanted to break someone's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.98,0:55:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为喝酒  发脾气以及愤怒\N'cause the drinking and the temper and the anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.95,0:55:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都是他遗传给我的\Nthose things in me were his.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.61,0:55:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是我对他的全部了解\NAnd they were all I could know of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.49,0:55:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在  我对他的了解有所不同\NBut now, well, now I get to know him a little different...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.16,0:55:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他也曾站在这样的一个房间里\N'cause he also stood in a room like this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.71,0:55:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,希望为了我和我妈好起来\Nwanting to get well for me and my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.05,0:55:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他手里握着这样的纪念章\NAnd he held the chip in his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.43,0:55:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写着五个月\Nand the chip said five months,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.76,0:55:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在那天  他...\Nand on that day, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.39,0:56:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在一切发生之前\NBefore it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.35,0:56:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那天  他最大的愿望\NWell, on that day, all he wanted in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.15,0:56:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是站在我今天所站的位置\Nwas to stand where I'm standing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.82,0:56:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而我做到了  所以\NAnd here I am, so
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.32,0:56:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家给我们两个的机会\Nthank you for us both, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.07,0:56:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也是杰克·托伦斯的\NThis is for Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.26,0:56:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,查理\NHey, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.56,0:56:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\NDoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.44,0:56:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我不需要问你为什么这个时候来\NGuess I don't need to ask why you're here at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.15,0:56:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你疼吗\NDo you have pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.11,0:56:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要我去找克劳戴特给你拿药吗\NDo you want me to get Claudette to bring you a pill?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.95,0:57:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,药没用了\NPill won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.00,0:57:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过你的上门服务\NI heard about these house calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.63,0:57:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,睡梦医生来拜访的真实原因\NWhat a visit from Doctor Sleep really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.26,0:57:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你都看到了什么  医生\NSo, what do you see, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.02,0:57:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了你的双胞胎儿子\NI see your twin sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.60,0:57:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,四岁\NFour years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.94,0:57:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到他们吗\NCan you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.11,0:57:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.78,0:57:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,法尔毛拖拉机\NFarmall tractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.03,0:57:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,座位上有一把条纹雨伞\NA striped umbrella over the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.28,0:57:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,五岁\NFive years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.79,0:57:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,拉着红色的小车\Npulling a red wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.16,0:57:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊  快瞧瞧\NLord, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.63,0:57:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一副纸牌\NLike a deck of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.84,0:57:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,全部按序排列\NAll out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.26,0:57:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不害怕地狱  医生\NI'm not scared of hell, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.68,0:58:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我度过了体面的一生\NUh, I lived a decent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.02,0:58:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再说我觉得并没有地狱\NI don't think there is such a place anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.27,0:58:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我只是害怕\NI guess I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.86,0:58:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,化为虚无\Nthere's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.49,0:58:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,从虚无中出生\NThere was nothing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.66,0:58:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,万一  死后也是虚无呢\NSo, what if there's nothing after?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.54,0:58:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,生命没有终点  查理\NWe don't end, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.58,0:58:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常确定\NI know that for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.79,0:58:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的东西我了解不多  但是\NI don't know much else... but
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.96,0:58:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道生命没有终点\NI know that we don't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.60,0:58:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝莓\NBlueberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.51,0:58:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能尝到我妈妈从前种的蓝莓\NI can taste blueberries my mother used to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.19,0:58:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你能尝到吗\NCan you taste them?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.94,0:58:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我尝到了\NYeah, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.86,0:58:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能听到你那台老收音机里放着法兰克的歌\NAnd I can hear Frank on your old radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.90,0:59:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是把它放在工具台上  摆在工具旁边\NThe one you used to have on your workbench next to your tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.28,0:59:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,? 和我一起翱翔 ?\N? Come fly with me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.70,0:59:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,? 一起翱翔  飞到远方 ?\N? Let's fly, let's fly away ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.41,0:59:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,? 如果想要喝到异域的琼浆 ?\N? If you can use Some exotic booze ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.79,0:59:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,? 在遥远的孟买有一家酒吧 ?\N? There's a bar in far Bombay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.88,0:59:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,? 和我一起翱翔 ?\N? Come fly with me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.01,0:59:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,? 一起翱翔 ?\N? Let's fly, let's fly... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.51,0:59:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,? 飞到远方 ?\N? Away ?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.95,0:59:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.73,0:59:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见  笔友\NBeen a minute, little pen pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.33,0:59:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,上学
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.21,0:59:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉  该上学了\NAbra? School.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.46,0:59:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我知道\NFine, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.90,1:00:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大爷  看到萝西了吗\NHey, Gramps, you seen Rosie?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.03,1:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,了望塔\NWatchtower.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.99,1:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NYou feelin' okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.99,1:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好得不得了\NPeachy keen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.47,1:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰你了\NSorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.97,1:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有收获吗\NAny luck?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.06,1:00:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快了\NGettin' closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.19,1:00:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他应该在爱荷华\NHe's somewhere in Iowa, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.11,1:01:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他后  我们就要开始长途公路旅行\NWe'll all take a nice long road trip once I'm sure I've found him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.78,1:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在我找到他之前  我们\NUntil I do, we...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.91,1:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你得开一个罐子  萝西\NYou gotta open a canister, Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.62,1:01:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们六个月前吸过灵气  乌鸦\NWe took steam six months ago, Crow.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.64,1:01:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,六个月算不了什么\NSix months is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.66,1:01:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,特拉华州那孩子灵气不够强\NThat kid in Delaware wasn't so steamy
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.64,1:01:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而且已经开始显现了\Nand it's already showing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.71,1:01:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到弗力克大爷的头发了吗\NYou see Grampa Flick's hair, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.54,1:01:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.67,1:01:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他状态不太好\NI don't think he's well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.63,1:01:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克松执政的时候弗力克大爷就不太好了\NGrampa Flick hasn't been well since Nixon was in office.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.34,1:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.47,1:01:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们需要进食  所有人都需要\NBut we need to eat. All of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.97,1:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,罐子不够了吗\NAre the canisters low?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.93,1:01:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是\N'Course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.98,1:01:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就能猎杀了  没必要再浪费一个\NJust no need to waste one if you're close to the kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.48,1:01:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西\NRosie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.98,1:01:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能需要进食才能找到他\NI might need it just to find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.24,1:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,以前世界上的灵气比现在要多\NThere used to be more steam in the world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.66,1:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别傻了  得了吧\NOh, don't be daft. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.79,1:01:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,正如凡人们说的\NThat's like when rubes say,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.91,1:01:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"五十年前  邻里之前友好得多"\N"50 years ago, people used to be more neighborly."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.71,1:01:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是事实  萝西\NBut it's true, Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.96,1:01:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上的灵气越来越少  也越来越微弱\NThere's less steam out there, and it's weaker, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.58,1:02:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道是因为他们的手机还是饮食\NI don't know if it's their cell phones or diets
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.50,1:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,又或是电视剧什么的\Nor their Netflix or what,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.67,1:02:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近都感觉不到他们了\Nbut I am not picking up many scents these days,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.09,1:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我能感受到  萝西  也没有那么...\Nand the ones that I do, Rosie, are just not that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.59,1:02:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我开一个罐子帮大家度过难关\NI'll open a canister tonight to tide everyone over.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.80,1:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.73,1:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道吗  萝西  -知道什么\N- You know it, Rosie. - I know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.02,1:02:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你每天都到这上面来的原因\NIt's why you're up here every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.31,1:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你对大家怎么说  你每天都会上来\NIt's why you're always up here no matter what you tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.03,1:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界灵气不再充裕\NThe world's not as steamy
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.66,1:02:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在寻找一个灵气强大的人\Nand you are looking for a whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.46,1:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爱荷华州  阿代尔
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.41,1:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你看那个孩子  十九号\NOh, watch this kid. Number 19.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.75,1:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子是个天才\NThat kid is a natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.92,1:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他每次都能击中球\NHe hits the ball every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.96,1:03:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就像能看透投手的想法一样\NLike he can read the pitcher's mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.50,1:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\NIs that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.97,1:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吧  早晚有一天  会有球探\NSee? You watch, one of these days, one of those talent scouts
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.18,1:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,听说这个布莱德  你就等着瞧吧\Nis gonna get wind of Brad there. You watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.62,1:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  十九号\NHey, 19,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.34,1:04:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才看了你的比赛\Njust saw your game.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.71,1:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经可以参加职业联赛了\NYou are ready for the majors.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.63,1:04:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-打得真漂亮  -谢谢\N- Well played. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.55,1:04:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要回家吗\NHey, you headin' home?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.47,1:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上车吗  我载你一程\NYou wanna hop in? I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.80,1:04:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  挺近的\NNo, it's real close.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.97,1:04:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\NI'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.69,1:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.27,1:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友  你想上车  我们带你回家\NWe're friends. You wanna hop in. We'll take you right home.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.57,1:04:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以带我回家\NYou can take me right home.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.24,1:04:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信我\NYou trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.61,1:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你\NI trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.94,1:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  求你了  不要\NNo! No, please! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.96,1:05:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不  求你们放了我\NNo! Please let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.87,1:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会说出去的  求你们了\NPlease, I won't tell. Please. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.17,1:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,十九号\NNumber 19.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.26,1:05:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子  你很出色\NKid, you were good.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.47,1:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.31,1:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,求你们了  放我走吧\NNo, please let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.19,1:05:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会说出去的  求你们了\NI won't tell. I won't tell. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.11,1:05:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.15,1:05:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,求你们了\NPlease.
