Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.87,1:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.73,1:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,灵气强吗\NBig steam?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.07,1:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  灵气极强\NOh, honey, it was huge.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.55,1:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.93,1:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是东海岸\NEast Coast, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.04,1:11:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说有人在2400公里之外窥视了我们\NYou're saying someone looked in from 1,500 miles away?
