Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.43,1:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她很快就离开了\NShe was out of there so fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.65,1:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我发誓  乌鸦老爹\NBut I swear, Crow Daddy,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.58,1:11:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没感受到过这样的力量\NI haven't felt power like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.16,1:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样原始的力量\Nraw power like that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.94,1:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太久没有过了\Nin so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.33,1:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们需要调查一下\NThen we need to look into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.51,1:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-越快越好  -对\N- Sooner the better. - Yeah.
