Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.38,1:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会抑制她...\NMight muffle her just...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.11,1:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,给这孩子吃帕罗西汀\NNo, giving Paxil to this kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.89,1:11:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就象是在探照灯上包上保鲜膜\Nit's like throwing a piece of Saran Wrap over a searchlight.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.62,1:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道她在哪\NI don't know where she is,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.70,1:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等她下次再来  她一定会再来的\Nbut when she comes back, and she'll be back,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.90,1:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我会准备好的  亲爱的\Noh, I'll be ready, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.39,1:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会准备好的\NI'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.43,1:12:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀\N谁\N棒球男孩
