Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.68,1:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫丹\NHis name's Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.35,1:13:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  学校的吗\NYeah? At school?
