Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.56,1:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他住得很近\NI mean, he lives close.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.36,1:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是在弗雷泽\NFrazier, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.72,1:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的\NNo big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.32,1:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布  你还好吗\NAbs, are you okay?
