Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.89,1:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚的事很抱歉\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.01,1:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的脑子有时候就像无线电\NI know that head of yours is like a radio sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.73,1:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你会收听到一些奇怪的频道\NAnd you pick up some weird stations.
