Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.24,1:14:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跑阵  传给十一号然后\NRunning play. Hand-off to 11 and...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.67,1:14:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,记不住的话教练会杀了我的\NCoach is gonna kill me if I don't get these.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.05,1:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么不喜欢我\NWhy doesn't he like me?
