Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.97,1:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NWell, I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.01,1:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西\NRosie?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.28,1:20:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有麻烦了\NWe've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.47,1:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-跟我说说  -那个窥视者\N- Talk to me. - The looker?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.07,1:20:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她又找到我了\NYeah, she found me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.03,1:20:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么会  -我不知道\N- How? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.37,1:20:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.83,1:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得抓到她  乌鸦  必须抓到\NWe have to have her, Crow. We have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.52,1:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道你是谁  我们在哪吗\NDoes she know who you are? Where we are?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.81,1:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不知道  应该没有...\NNo, I don't know. I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.40,1:20:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那不重要  听着\NThat's not the important... Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.91,1:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-我说她的灵气很强  对吧  -嗯\N- I said she's huge steam, right? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.37,1:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上比那还强\NYeah, it's even bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.80,1:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我试图在她脑中与她对抗\NI tried to turn around in her
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.09,1:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而她不费吹灰之力就把我赶了出来\Nand she blew me out of her like I was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.40,1:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-胡说吧  -不  我从未有过这种遭遇\N- Bullshit. - No. Never happened to me, ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.37,1:21:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前会说这不可能\NI would have said that was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.04,1:21:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是要吃了她  还是转化她\NIs she food or do we turn her?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.02,1:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不转化她\NWe don't turn her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.65,1:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西  你确定吗\NRosie, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.29,1:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她真如你所说  那...\NIf she's what you say she is, then...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.54,1:21:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真结族里面不能允许有这种能力的人\NThen we don't want anyone with that power in the Knot.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.95,1:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  好好想想\NJeez. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.71,1:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,万一她都不是呢\NWhat if she's neither?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.95,1:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.21,1:21:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不杀她\NI mean, we don't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.83,1:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也不转化她\NAnd we don't turn her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.89,1:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想想如果是一头奶牛\NThink of a cow.
