Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.72,1:21:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让它活着\NKeep it alive,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.43,1:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好好照顾\Ntake care of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.82,1:21:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,能喝几年的牛奶\Nit gives you milk for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.58,1:21:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-萝西  我们从没那么做过  -我知道\N- Rosie, we've never tried that. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.61,1:21:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有灵气的头脑很危险\NBecause a steam head is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.78,1:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让它活着  可能会有危险\NYou keep it alive, it could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.16,1:22:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  重点...\NI know. The point...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.80,1:22:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,乌鸦  重点是\NThe point, Crow,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.54,1:22:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我的大白鲸\Nis she's the great white whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.66,1:22:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要她\NAnd I want her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.00,1:22:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要她\NI want her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.05,1:22:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈要她\NI fucking want her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.32,1:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第四章
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.07,1:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,转化  世界
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.89,1:22:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你今天愉快\NHave a great day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.30,1:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是\NYou, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.73,1:23:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.62,1:24:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,比利\NBilly.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.57,1:24:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到我的声音\NYou can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.13,1:24:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是开口说话吧  好吗\NLet's use our outside voices, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.92,1:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你追踪到了我\NYou tracked me down?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.22,1:24:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比我想得容易  像我大脑中有导航系统一样\NIt was easier than I thought. Like GPS, but in my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.31,1:24:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我无意冒犯  但在如今\NLook, I don't mean any offense, but this day and age,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.63,1:24:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一个成年男子和一个小女孩坐在公园长椅上...\Na grown man sitting with a teenage girl on a park bench...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.25,1:24:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿布拉·斯通  有人问起  你就是我叔叔\NI'm Abra Stone. And if anyone asks, you're my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.42,1:24:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,丹叔叔\NUncle Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.21,1:24:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不是撒谎  不完全是\NAnd that's not even a lie. Not totally.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.70,1:24:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在别的方面也算有关系\NWe're related in other ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.76,1:25:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你像我一样有魔法\NYou're magic, like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.21,1:25:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不了解魔法\NI don't know about magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.08,1:25:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.66,1:25:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直管它叫闪灵\NI always called it the shining.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.53,1:25:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们都有闪灵能力\NAnd, yeah, we both shine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.33,1:25:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母知道吗\NDo your parents know?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.76,1:25:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的闪灵能力\NAbout my shine?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.78,1:25:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们害怕\NThey're scared of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.98,1:25:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们以为能力消失了  除了几件事\Nbut they think it's gone except for a few things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.25,1:25:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,比如我妈妈有时会让我帮她\NLike, my mom sometimes asks me to help her
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.64,1:25:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,找她弄丢的东西\Nfind something she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.43,1:25:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上个月  是她的车钥匙\NLast month, it was her car keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.10,1:25:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她落在了车库里我爸爸的工作台上\NShe left them on my dad's worktable in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.06,1:25:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们避而不谈\NBut they don't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.64,1:25:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我使用能力  他们会用异样的眼神看我\NOr if I use it, they look at me different.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.87,1:25:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,或者完全不看我\NOr not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.70,1:25:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次一整天都没看我\NNot for a whole day once.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.27,1:25:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不肯直视我的眼睛\NWouldn't look me in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.28,1:25:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我尽力不去使用\NSo, I try not to use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.33,1:25:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果别人发现了\NBecause if people find out,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.44,1:25:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会认为我是个怪胎  知道吧\N"Eek, a freak." You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.07,1:25:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定知道\NSure you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.90,1:25:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你也尽力不去使用\NYou try not to use it, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.88,1:25:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经坚持很久了\NYou've been trying a long time,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.17,1:26:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她也不肯直视你的眼睛\Nand she couldn't look you in your eyes either.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.42,1:26:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候\NWhen I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.23,1:26:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不理解闪灵  我叫它"托尼"\NI didn't understand the shining. I called it "Tony."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.79,1:26:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他是我的幻想好友\NI thought he was my imaginary friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.12,1:26:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你是我的幻想好友\NI thought you were my imaginary friend...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.31,1:26:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那样想了很久\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.57,1:26:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样的人有多少\NHow many of us are out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.18,1:26:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都有一点闪灵能力\NThere's a lot of people who have a little bit of shine,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.18,1:26:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们自己都不知道\Nthey don't even know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.79,1:26:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总在妻子伤心时\NThey always seem to come home with flowers
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.30,1:26:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,正好带着花回家\Nwhen their wives are sad,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.45,1:26:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,或者没有复习就考得很好\Nor they do well on the school test they didn't study for.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.33,1:26:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我一辈子也只认识\NBut I only met two or three people
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.72,1:26:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,两三个知道自己有闪灵能力的人\Nin my whole life who knew they shined.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.75,1:26:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,棒球男孩有闪灵能力\NThe baseball boy shined.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.14,1:26:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫布莱德利·特雷弗\NHis name was Bradley Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.05,1:26:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人\NThese people...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.37,1:26:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看起来都不像人  抓走了他\Nthey look like people anyway, they took him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.12,1:26:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吃了他\NAnd they ate him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.44,1:26:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吃了他的闪灵\NThey ate his shine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.99,1:26:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以感觉到吗\NYou could feel it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.59,1:27:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们能感觉到我\NAnd they could feel me, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.09,1:27:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,至少其中一位能  一位女士\NAt least one of them did. A lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.03,1:27:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,戴帽子的女士\NThe lady with the hat.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.97,1:27:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找到他们  阻止他们\NI wanna find them, stop them,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.29,1:27:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得他们杀害过其他很多孩子\Nbecause I think they've done this to a lot of other kids, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.41,1:27:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得做些什么  对吧\NSo, I have to do something, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.61,1:27:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要来这里\NWhy did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.78,1:27:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是我\NWhy me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.31,1:27:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你能听到我的声音\NBecause you can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.01,1:27:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你会相信我  你也有闪灵能力\NYou'd believe me. You shine, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.01,1:27:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们伤害我们这样的人\NAnd they hurt people like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.77,1:27:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做\NI mean, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.63,1:27:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能拿到他身上的东西\NIf you could get something of his,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.99,1:27:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能去爱荷华\Nif you could go to Iowa...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.08,1:27:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-等等  -我可以帮你找到他\N- Whoa, hang on. - I can help you find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.23,1:27:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那样他的父母就能知道他的下落\NThen his parents would know where he was.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.81,1:27:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,至少可以好好埋葬他\NThey could bury him right, at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.85,1:27:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还可以拿到他的手套\NWe could also get his glove.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.99,1:27:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能碰到手套  就可以追踪他们\NIf I can touch that glove, I can track them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.96,1:27:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等\NEasy. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.73,1:27:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大块头巴里  那人好像叫这个名字\NBecause Barry the Chunk, I think that was his name,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.08,1:27:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们杀死他之前的一段时间\Nfor a while, before they killed him,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.40,1:27:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那人戴过他的手套\Nhe was wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.42,1:28:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉  回家去\NAbra, go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.64,1:28:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,想想你的学业  想想你的父母\NThink about your school. Think about your parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.09,1:28:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想想你的余生\NThink about the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.47,1:28:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别追踪这些人\NDon't chase these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.24,1:28:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别激怒他们\NDon't aggravate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.11,1:28:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何  都不要吸引他们的注意力\NAnd whatever you do, don't attract their attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.40,1:28:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别使用闪灵能力\NDon't shine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.97,1:28:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想想办法  任何办法\NFind something, anything...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.72,1:28:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多是任何办法吧  阻止你的闪灵\NWell, almost anything, to stop that shine of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.74,1:28:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,低调行事  掩藏你的闪灵  祈求上帝\NKeep your head down, keep your shine down and hope to God
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.40,1:28:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让那些人  或者类似的生物\Nthat these people or anything like them,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.82,1:28:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不会发现你\Nthat they don't see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.07,1:28:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们发现了你  他们会回来\NIf they see you, they come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.59,1:28:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉  你明白吗\NAbra, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.33,1:28:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会回来\NThey come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.91,1:28:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,低调行事  注意安全\NKeep your head down. Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.69,1:28:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.30,1:29:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那年很不容易\NThings were tough that year.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.13,1:29:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很多演员都失业了\NA lot of actors were out of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.17,1:29:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好\NHey, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.36,1:29:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,杂耍大明星埃尔默·福德来了\NHere comes Elmer Fudd that big vaudeville star.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.44,1:29:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.25,1:29:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  医生\NOh, it's nothing, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.71,1:29:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.72,1:29:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想起爸爸了\NThinking about Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.44,1:29:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\NNo, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.00,1:29:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有  而且你不愿想起\NYou are. And you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.94,1:29:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心我  医生\NDon't worry about me, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.48,1:29:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.38,1:29:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都没事\NWe're fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.41,1:30:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,阿兹\NHey, Azzie.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.95,1:30:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚搞错了吧\NYou got your wires crossed tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.88,1:30:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个空房间  阿兹\NThat room's empty, Az.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.10,1:30:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那房间里没人\NThere's no one in that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.37,1:31:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  医生\NWhoa! Hang on, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.98,1:31:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克\NDick.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.92,1:31:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NOh, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.91,1:31:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我还以为是...\NI... I... I thought it was...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.10,1:31:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我是眺望酒店里那些东西\NThought I was from the Overlook.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.31,1:31:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,差点把我锁起来\NAlmost locked me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.45,1:31:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那些老鬼魂还来找你吗\NStill getting visits from them old ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.10,1:31:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  好几年都没来了\NNo, not for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.90,1:31:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,霍勒斯·德文特是最后一位\NHorace Derwent was the last one,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.36,1:31:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他的西装上都是五彩纸屑\Nconfetti on his suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.25,1:31:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,和我说  "派对很棒吧"\NSaid, "Great party, isn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.40,1:31:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,脸上挂着欠揍的笑容  直到我把他关进盒子\NShit-eating grin on his face till I pulled out a box for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.85,1:31:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的笑容消失得很快\NThat grin went fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.47,1:31:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我过去一直都没想到要问你\NHey, it never occurred to me to ask you back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.12,1:31:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们关进盒子后会怎么样\NWhat happens to them in those boxes?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.90,1:31:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会死在里面吗\NDo they die in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.43,1:31:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在乎吗\NDo you care?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.98,1:31:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你了\NI missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.18,1:31:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很久没见了吗\NHas it been a long time?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.95,1:31:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我分不清\NCan't tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.36,1:31:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界现在对我来说是一个梦中梦\NThis world is a dream of a dream to me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.28,1:31:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,八年多一点\NEight years. Little more.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.96,1:31:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上次我见你时\NLast time I saw you,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.00,1:31:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你陷入了低谷\Nyou was at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.13,1:31:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看起来好多了\NYou look better now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.02,1:32:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么来这里\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.22,1:32:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里是因为一切都是轮回\NI'm here because it all comes 'round.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.81,1:32:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,灵魂周而复始  医生\NKa's a wheel, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.78,1:32:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了  孩子\NYou listen, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.36,1:32:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里很痛苦  所以我只说一次\NIt hurts to be here, so I'll only say it once.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.44,1:32:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那些空洞的恶魔\NThese empty devils ever found you
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.69,1:32:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在你小时候找到了你\Nwhen you was a tyke,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.54,1:32:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们嗅到你的一丝气息\Nif they'd even sniffed you,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.94,1:32:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就死了\Nyou'd be long dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.84,1:32:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就象是大地患上的癌症\NThey're on the land like a cancer on the skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.88,1:32:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们曾在沙漠里骑骆驼\NOnce, they rode camels in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.59,1:32:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也曾组织车队穿越东欧\NOnce, they drove caravans across Eastern Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.99,1:32:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以尖叫为食\NThey eat screams,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.43,1:32:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以痛苦为饮\Nand drink pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.87,1:32:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经注意到了那个小女孩\Nand they've noticed that little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.91,1:32:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能会杀了她\NThey might kill her,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.91,1:32:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会转化她\Nmight turn her,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.08,1:32:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或者养着她  直到她被榨干\Nor might keep her till she's all used up,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.95,1:32:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是最坏的情况\Nand that'd be worst of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.57,1:32:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能让他们得逞\NYou can't let 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.84,1:33:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是我\NWhy me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.83,1:33:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她找到了你\NBecause she found you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.02,1:33:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她出现了  见鬼  医生  为什么是我\NBecause she showed up. Hell, Doc, why me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.76,1:33:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有一天突然走进我的厨房\NYou just walked on into my kitchen one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.06,1:33:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,到现在我都解脱不了\Nand I'm still on the hook.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.68,1:33:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底该怎么做\NWhat the hell am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.79,1:33:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她要什么就给她\NGet her what she asked for.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.40,1:33:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会再见到我了  医生\NYou won't see me again, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.53,1:33:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我最后的梦\NThis is my last dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.72,1:33:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你成长为一个好人了  孩子\NIt seems to me you grew up fine, son,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.52,1:33:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但你还欠一笔债\Nbut you still owe a debt.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.34,1:33:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还清它\NPay it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.11,1:33:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼  什么事\NGod, damn it. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.55,1:34:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了\NSorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.32,1:34:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你"不许打扰我"  是不是\NI told you, "No distractions." Didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.47,1:34:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃不喝\NNothing to eat, nothing to drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.28,1:34:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,安宁平静地冥想\NJust peace, quiet, and meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.41,1:34:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚要集中精力对付她  乌鸦\NI need all my wits for her tonight, Crow.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.31,1:34:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才要来  我有发现\NThat's why I'm here. I found something.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.79,1:34:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,安尼斯顿发生小型地震
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.82,1:34:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最微弱的地震能有多微弱\N"How small can an earthquake be?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.64,1:34:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安尼斯顿的里奇兰街在索科河中断\NPretty small, if the people of Richland Court,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.40,1:34:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那里的居民可信\Na short Anniston street that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.70,1:34:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么地震可以非常微弱\Ndead-ends at the Saco River, are to be believed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.96,1:34:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,周二深夜\NLate Tuesday night,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.08,1:34:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这条街上几名居民称有地震\Nseveral residents of the street reported a tremor
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.52,1:34:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,致使窗户作响  地板摇晃\Nthat rattled windows, shook floors,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.49,1:34:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,架子上的玻璃器具滚落\Nand sent glassware tumbling from the shelves.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.17,1:34:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管伦瑟姆的地质监测中心\NAlthough the Geological Survey Center in Wrentham
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.31,1:34:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,报告上周二新英格兰地区没有地震"\Nreports there were no temblors in New England last Tuesday."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.36,1:34:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.71,1:34:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  也许吧\NI think, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.61,1:35:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不能百分百确定  但有五成可能也不错\NI'm not a hundred percent, but I'll take fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.91,1:35:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那真的是她\NIf that's actually her...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.17,1:35:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,里奇兰街\NRichland Court.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.67,1:35:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是她摇动了新罕布什尔的整条街\NShe did that, shook a whole street in New Hampshire...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.02,1:35:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个可以集中调查的地方\NHaving a place to actually focus on,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.60,1:35:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一个城镇  而是一条街\Nnot just a town, but a street,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.76,1:35:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,会让我今晚容易得多\Nis gonna make things a hell of a lot easier for me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.53,1:35:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,查得好\NGood catch.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.15,1:35:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么对付她\NHow you coming at her?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.78,1:35:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候她睡着了\NWell, she'll be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.64,1:35:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我探查一下  看看是不是她\NI'll just wanna look around, see if she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.83,1:35:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,植入一些暗示  如同小虫子\NPlant some suggestions, like little worms.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.19,1:35:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,让它们挖掘\NLet them burrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.87,1:35:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一百条关于她亲爱的朋友  真结族的虫子\NA hundred worms about her dear friends, the Knot.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.93,1:35:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们出现\NAnd when we roll up,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.41,1:35:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她会高兴得迫不及待跳上车\Nshe'll be so happy to see us, she'll just hop right in the van.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.59,1:35:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是她干的\NIf she did this...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.93,1:35:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她真的摇动了整条街\Nreally shook a whole street,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.74,1:36:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该小心点\NI think you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.07,1:36:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是个小女孩\NShe's a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.19,1:36:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而你永远是最凶悍的女王\NAnd you are the queen bitch of all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.40,1:36:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.55,1:36:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说说\NJust saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.86,1:36:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.62,1:36:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMom.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.62,1:36:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉还好吗\NYou feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.15,1:36:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你没下来吃晚饭\NWe missed you at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.18,1:36:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺好  只是今天过得不顺\NI'm okay. Just had a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.72,1:36:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我明早要坐飞机去看奶奶\NI'm flying out to see momo in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.57,1:36:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽早回来\NI'll be back as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.23,1:37:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布  她...\NAbs, is she...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.68,1:37:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她这次能挺过去吗\NIs she gonna pull through this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.77,1:37:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.39,1:37:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望能\NI hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.71,1:37:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她我爱她\NTell her I love her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.45,1:40:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,接着睡  公主\NKeep sleeping, princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.31,1:40:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些凡人\NYou rubes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.48,1:40:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一辈子都在做小盒子\NSpend your whole lives making little boxes,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.03,1:40:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,渺小的记忆\Nlittle memories.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.81,1:40:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们以为这样就无比充实了\NOh, you think they make you so rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.20,1:40:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你真该看看我的  孩子\NYou should see mine, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.89,1:40:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脑子就像个大教堂\NOh, my mind's a cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.27,1:40:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\NWell, hi there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.02,1:41:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你会回来的\NHe said you'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.28,1:41:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的确回来了\NAnd you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.16,1:41:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.70,1:41:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.93,1:41:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,退后  退后\NGet back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.69,1:41:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是个小孩\NYou're just a fucking child!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.02,1:41:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.80,1:41:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里  你在哪里  哪里\NWhere? Where did you...? Where...?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.76,1:41:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里  你在哪里\NWhat did you...? Where did you...?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.75,1:41:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.94,1:41:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,出去  出去\NGet out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.89,1:41:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.66,1:42:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西\NRose?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.91,1:42:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱\NTrap.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.28,1:42:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱\NTrap.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.92,1:42:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\NWhat the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.36,1:42:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-那小贱人给我设了个陷阱  -老天  你的手\N- Little bitch set a trap for me. - Oh, my God. Your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.51,1:42:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西  萝西  冷静\NRose! Rose, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.10,1:42:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道她在哪里了  对吗  我们现在知道了\NWe know where she is now, right? Now we know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.18,1:42:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她刚刚在我脑子里\NShe was in my head!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.72,1:42:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -偷东西\N- What? - Stealing!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.27,1:42:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道了什么\NWhat does she know?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.58,1:42:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不知道\NI don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.85,1:42:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-她知道了多少...  -我不知道\N- How much does she... - I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.44,1:42:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道  -出了个问题\N- I don't know... - There's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.58,1:42:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不行\NNot now!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.82,1:42:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,弗力克大爷\NGrampa Flick...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.92,1:42:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他开始循环了\NI think he's cycling.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.01,1:43:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,丹叔叔  丹叔叔  我伤到她了\NUncle Dan! Uncle Dan, I hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.03,1:43:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的伤到她了\NI really hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.22,1:43:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我伤到她了  她活该\NI hurt her and she deserved it
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.45,1:43:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不是最棒的  最棒的是...\Nand that's not the best part. The best part is...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.04,1:43:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒的是我进入了她的脑子  我进入了她的脑子\NThe best part is I got in her head. I got in her head.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.01,1:43:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-丹叔叔  你听到了吗  -天呐  阿布拉\N- Uncle Dan? Are you there? - Oh, God, Abra.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.24,1:43:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到吗\NCan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.22,1:43:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么\NWhat have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.68,1:43:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟那孩子聊聊吧\NJust talk to the kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.52,1:43:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们要做的话  那就豁出去了\NIf we're gonna do this, then let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.22,1:43:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  阿布拉\NHi, Abra.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.30,1:43:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我听得到\NI can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.15,1:43:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.95,1:43:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你会明白的\NYou will.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.11,1:44:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我们永生不死\NI thought we lived forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.98,1:44:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有人跟你这么保证过吗  安蒂\NDid someone promise you that, Andi?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.73,1:44:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有人说过你不朽不灭吗\NDid someone say you're immortal?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.33,1:44:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是"长生不老  吃得好"\NI said, "Live long, eat well."
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.31,1:44:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能活得很久  非常久\NWe can live long, very long.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.38,1:44:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的确如此\NAnd we do,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.42,1:44:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,绝大多数如此\Nmost of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.13,1:44:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们吃得不好\NBut we haven't been eating well.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.45,1:44:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很长时间了\NNot for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.64,1:44:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西  他不行了\NRosie, he's going.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.41,1:44:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西\NRosie.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.59,1:44:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  亲爱的\NYes, love?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.16,1:44:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕\NI'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.92,1:44:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你不害怕\NNo, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.93,1:44:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你目睹过王朝的兴衰\NYou watched empires rise and fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.24,1:44:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在罗马为角斗士喝彩\NCheered the gladiators in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.92,1:44:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,扬帆大海\NSailed across oceans,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.27,1:44:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,驶向新世界\Nto new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.29,1:44:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾猎食国王  王子  教皇\Nwhile you fed on kings, and princes, and popes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.45,1:45:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,人们书写你的传说\NThey wrote myths of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.10,1:45:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为你塑雕像\Nand made statues,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.54,1:45:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在村庄里  被窝里\Nand they trembled in their villages, and beds,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.38,1:45:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,摩天大楼里战栗\Nand skyscrapers.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.22,1:45:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\NSo, no...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.84,1:45:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不害怕\Nyou're not scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.98,1:45:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是王\NYou're a king...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.70,1:45:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你以恐惧为食\Nand you eat fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.93,1:46:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟\NHey, bro.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.09,1:46:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是凌晨四点\NYou know, it's 4:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.48,1:46:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我朝夕相处  比利\NYou've always seen me, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.62,1:46:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看人很准  这么说对吗\NYou have a good sense about people, is that fair to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.40,1:46:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对  怎么...\NYeah, what...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.90,1:46:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我诚实吗  是好人吗\NYou think I'm an honest man? A good man?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.62,1:46:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是  是  丹  我...\NI do, I do. Dan, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.07,1:46:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙\NI need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.53,1:46:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,首先需要你听我讲个故事\NThe first thing I need is for you to listen to a story
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.25,1:46:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,并且尽你所能去相信我\Nand try harder than you've ever tried to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.18,1:46:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如何\NHow's it going?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.62,1:46:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是该准备上学了吗\NShouldn't you be getting ready for school?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.35,1:47:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但我想跟着\NYeah, but I wanted to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.04,1:47:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你开了多久了\NHow long have you been driving?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.51,1:47:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,几个小时吧\NA few hours or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.04,1:47:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天夜里应该能到\NWe should get there tonight. Late.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.61,1:47:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.33,1:47:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我朋友\NHe's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.55,1:47:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是我最好的朋友\NMaybe my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.67,1:47:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该看看她的脸\NYou should've seen her face.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.58,1:47:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她害怕了  丹叔叔\NShe was scared, Uncle Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.46,1:47:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那些孩子一样害怕\NScared like all those kids were scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.35,1:47:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那些被她杀害的孩子\NAll those kids she's killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.22,1:47:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的侵入让她既愤怒又恐惧\NShe was so mad and so scared that I got in.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.34,1:47:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个新招数\NThat was a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.81,1:47:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没那么做过\NI've never done that before.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.76,1:47:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没做过  那是什么感觉\NYeah, me neither. What was it like?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.28,1:47:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,像个图书馆\NLike a library.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.92,1:47:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我们内心都是图书馆\NI guess we're all libraries inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.15,1:47:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做的\NHow'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.69,1:47:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样  轻轻一推\NLike this. Just a little push.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.10,1:47:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.73,1:47:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起  对不起\NSorry! Sorry, sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.32,1:47:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起  我不是故意的  -没事\N- I'm sorry. I didn't mean to. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.72,1:47:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那些盒子都是什么\NWhat were all those boxes?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.59,1:48:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.69,1:48:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说谎\NLiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.04,1:48:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我小的时候\NWhen I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.34,1:48:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,比你还小的时候  我遇到了类似这样的东西\Nyounger than you, I bumped into something like these things
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.15,1:48:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,像他们一样吃人的东西\Nthat ate like they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.42,1:48:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过那不是人  是个地方\NOnly it wasn't a person, it was a place.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.24,1:48:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,后来他们封锁了那里  荒废了\NThey closed it down after and let it rot.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.95,1:48:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但住在那里的东西  他们...\NBut the things that lived there, they...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.34,1:48:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别再去那里乱转了\NDon't go poking around in there again.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.56,1:48:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我不去了  我保证\NOkay, I won't. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.38,1:48:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快准备好了  正在装车\NWe're almost ready. We're just loading up.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.47,1:48:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.02,1:48:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,开车上路\NGet the caravan on the road
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.11,1:48:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一两天内就能抓到她\Nand we'll have her in a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.91,1:48:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不该去  萝西\NI don't think you should come, Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.57,1:48:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈说什么\NThe fuck did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.25,1:48:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她瞄上了你\NShe tagged you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.74,1:48:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她进入过你的脑子\NShe got in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.06,1:49:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对  那不会再发生了\NYeah, it won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.04,1:49:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你把她赶出去前她摸清了多少\NAnd who knows how much she got to before you kicked her out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.87,1:49:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的  乌鸦\NShe's mine, Crow.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.07,1:49:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  据我们所知\NRight now, as far as we know,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.34,1:49:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我们中她唯一可以追踪的人\Nyou are the only one of us she could track.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.27,1:49:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她看到你要去了\NNow, if she sees you coming,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.16,1:49:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能会逃跑\Nshe could run
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.51,1:49:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,或者再设一个陷阱\Nor set another trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.87,1:49:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我会弄晕她\NI will knock her out cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.46,1:49:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在国家安全局的人给我弄了好货\NOne of our assets from the NSA gave me the good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.55,1:49:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能放倒她  不会有药物过量的风险\NPut her out without chance of an overdose.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.80,1:49:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我往南去  兜一圈\NI'll head south. I'll circle around.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.45,1:49:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,从另一个方向袭击她\NI'll come at her from a different direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.58,1:49:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该去的\NI should be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.79,1:49:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我说得对\NYou know I'm right about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.02,1:49:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.19,1:49:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要的话  我可以让安蒂留下陪你\NI'll leave Andi here with you, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.64,1:49:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你们需要全部的战力\NNo, no, you'll need your strength, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.82,1:49:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她对你们耍花招\NIf she pulls a trick on you,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.97,1:49:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,待在一起\Nstay together.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.99,1:49:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.39,1:49:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也有自己的招数\NBut I got some tricks of my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.42,1:49:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们到了\NHey, I think we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.62,1:50:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.28,1:50:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看看能不能联系上她\NI'll see if I can get her.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.17,1:50:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.82,1:50:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拉美克工业\N乙醇工厂\N东北入口\N关停待通知
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.83,1:50:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个标牌  绕去后面\NThat's the sign. Pull around back.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.77,1:50:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她说绕去后面\NShe says to pull around back.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.24,1:50:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你在哪停\NAnd I'll tell you when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.33,1:50:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她会告诉我们在哪停\NShe'll tell us when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.59,1:50:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说  丹\NI gotta tell you, Danno,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.47,1:50:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我希望你是对的还是错的\NI don't know whether I hope you're right or wrong about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.08,1:50:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是错的  那我朋友疯了\NI mean, if you're wrong, my friend is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.92,1:50:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,彻头彻尾地疯了\NI mean, full-blown, mental breakdown,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.62,1:50:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,幻想的怪物杀害幻想的小孩\Nimaginary-monsters- killing-imaginary-kids
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.86,1:50:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,疯了\Nbonkers.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.23,1:50:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不过...这我可以接受\NBut, you know, I... I can work with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.89,1:50:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你是对的...\NIf you're right, though...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.31,1:50:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.04,1:50:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就更糟了\NIt's much worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.88,1:51:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该回家去\NYou should go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.22,1:51:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.00,1:51:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是说你\NNo, not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.46,1:51:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我能应付\NI can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.72,1:51:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不  接下来就交给我们\NNo. We'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.44,1:51:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好  只有我们了\NOkay, it's just us.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.25,1:51:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你闻到了吗\NYou smell that?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.28,1:51:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前打过猎  跟你说过吗\NUsed to hunt. I ever tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.79,1:51:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.16,1:51:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,猎鹿\NDeer.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.77,1:51:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有个夏天\NThis one summer,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.35,1:51:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我打伤了一头公鹿\NI clipped this buck.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.12,1:51:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我追了它两天\NI was tracking it for two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.64,1:51:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,射中了  打伤了它\NI got the shot, clipped him.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.95,1:51:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它跑了  我去追\NHe ran off, I went after.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.29,1:52:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以为它不会坚持多久\NFigured he wasn't gonna last long.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.59,1:52:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后它消失了\NThen he vanished.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.26,1:52:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就那么失去踪影\NJust up and evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.26,1:52:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无痕迹  真的莫名其妙\NNot a trace. Truly baffling.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.65,1:52:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,五天后\NFive days later,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.06,1:52:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我在另一个地方打猎  隔了好几公里\NI'm trying a different spot, miles away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.06,1:52:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那里找掩蔽的地方\NI come around looking for a spot for a blind...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.32,1:52:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我闻到了它\Nthen I smelled him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.12,1:52:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,闻到了它\NSmelled him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.54,1:52:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了那头公鹿\NFound that buck
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.44,1:52:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在一个中空的树干里\Nholed up to a hollow trunk,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.69,1:52:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,死了好几天\Ndead for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.58,1:52:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那气味...\NThe smell...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.33,1:52:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从那以后我再不打猎\NNever hunted a day since.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.85,1:52:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是同样的气味\NThis is the same smell.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.66,1:53:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,比利\NBilly.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.58,1:53:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.36,1:53:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.88,1:53:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,操\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.84,1:54:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,操  丹  什么鬼\NFuck, Danno. What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.55,1:54:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至没有好好埋葬他  埋得很浅\NThey didn't even bury him deep. They buried him shallow.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.06,1:54:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  比利\NI'm sorry, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.76,1:54:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我们卷入什么事里了\NWhat did you get us into?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.70,1:54:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,第五章
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.44,1:54:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小戏法
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.98,1:54:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,杀害他的那些人\NThe people who did that...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.57,1:54:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是人\NThey're not people.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.09,1:54:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他们不是\NNo. No, they ain't.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.88,1:54:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,会这样伤害一个小男孩的人\NAnyone do that to a little boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.93,1:54:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都不是人\Nthey ain't people.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.09,1:54:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们找到了吗\NDid you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.45,1:54:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\NYeah, we got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.64,1:54:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她回来了吗\NIs she back?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.40,1:54:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在往你那里赶  早上就到\NWe're heading back to you. We'll be back in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.40,1:54:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中途要停一下\NWe got a stop to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.95,1:54:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你给你父母看看发生的事\NI need you to show your parents what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.03,1:54:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.83,1:54:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-要的  -不  他们几乎以为我正常了\N- Yeah. - No. They almost think I'm normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.07,1:54:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉他们  他们会...\NIf I tell them, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.32,1:54:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西会通过他们对付你\NRose'll go through them to get to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.24,1:54:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  不是吗\NYou know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.68,1:54:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她会毫不迟疑杀死他们\NShe'll cut them down without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.56,1:54:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而她要来了  阿布拉\NAnd she's coming, Abra.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.95,1:54:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要知道\NThey need to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.45,1:55:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在哪里停一下\NSo, what's this stop we gotta make?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.74,1:55:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还留着猎鹿的步枪吗\NYou still got those old deer rifles?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.46,1:55:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是丹叔叔吗\NYou're Uncle Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.21,1:55:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-你以为你是谁  -先生\N- The fuck you think you are? - Sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.45,1:55:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她才十三岁\NShe is 13 years old!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.52,1:55:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉  我告诉过你要给他看看\NAbra, I told you to show him.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.85,1:55:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-我告诉他了  -那不一样\N- I told him. - Well, that's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.27,1:55:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要痛揍你一顿  然后报警\NI'm gonna kick your ass before I call the police, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.38,1:55:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  阿布拉\NNo, no, no. Abra.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.27,1:55:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫她的名字\NNow, don't you say her name.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.41,1:55:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.53,1:55:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  斯通先生  我是你们的朋友\NI'm sorry, Mr. Stone. I am a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.99,1:55:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉你的事都是真的\NEverything she told you is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.19,1:56:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么\NWhat the hell is happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.01,1:56:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.62,1:56:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉需要给你看点东西\NAbra needs to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.11,1:56:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了那个男孩\NI saw the boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.39,1:56:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了他的尸体\NI saw his body.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.18,1:56:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,都是真的\NIt's all true.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.12,1:56:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能是你这个朋友把他埋在那里的\NProbably, your friend here put him there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.54,1:56:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你想过吗\NYou think about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.15,1:56:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没想太久\NNot for long, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.51,1:56:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,斯通先生  你的女儿很特别\NMr. Stone, your daughter is special.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.05,1:56:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不准谈论她\NDon't talk about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.89,1:56:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你内心深处知道\NI think you know that. Deep down.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.01,1:56:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道那个小男孩出了什么事\NShe knows what happened to that little boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.74,1:56:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她还知道是谁干的\Nand she knows who did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.49,1:56:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,给他看看\NShow him.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.88,1:56:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  爸爸\NI'm sorry, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.51,1:56:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不想\NI really didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.79,1:56:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不想做什么\NDidn't want to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.52,1:56:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  谢谢\NNo, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.45,1:57:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.91,1:57:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人\NThose people...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.86,1:57:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道我女儿的能力吗\Nthey know about my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.78,1:57:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,知道\NThey do.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.46,1:57:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们迟早会来\NAnd sooner or later, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.27,1:57:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须做点什么\NWe gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.57,1:57:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们报警  找联调局\NAll right, we're calling the police, the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.68,1:57:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人已经活了很久很久  先生\NThese people have been around a long, long time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.31,1:57:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有钱  有关系\NThey're rich, connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.87,1:57:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们根本不怕警察\NI don't think they're worried about the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.38,1:57:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们在哪\NBut where are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.05,1:57:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么时候来  我们能去哪\NWhen are they coming? Where can we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.50,1:57:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉能回答这些\NAbra can answer that...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.48,1:57:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只要她准备好了\Nif she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.07,1:57:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好了\NI'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.13,1:57:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定想这么做吗\NYou sure you wanna do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.12,1:57:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须做\NI have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.74,1:58:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I95公路\NI-95.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.43,1:58:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里  乌鸦  蛇  还有别的几个\NBarry, the Crow, the Snake, and a few others.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.26,1:58:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,树木看起来没什么不同\NThe trees haven't changed that much,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.70,1:58:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以或许在马萨诸塞\Nso maybe Massachusetts,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.40,1:58:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-不过他们很近了  -萝西呢\N- but they're close. - Rose?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.31,1:58:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没看到她\NDidn't see her.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.13,1:58:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们要来了\NBut they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.47,1:58:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是她唯一看到的房间吗\NThis is the only room she saw?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.12,1:58:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.36,1:58:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了些改变  藏了几样东西\NAnd I made a few changes. Hid a few things.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.69,1:59:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.71,1:59:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会试图追踪你\NWell, they'll be trying to track you,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.04,1:59:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,试图搞明白\Ntrying to catch on.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.61,1:59:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而你要让他们得逞\NAnd you're gonna let them.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.37,1:59:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗\NAre you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.77,1:59:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧  但你要让他们得逞\NPossibly, but you're gonna let them.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.13,1:59:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我需要你变个戏法\NAnd then I need you to try and do a little trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.53,1:59:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,变魔法吗\NA magic trick?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.01,1:59:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在跟踪我们\NThey're following us.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.85,1:59:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,集中注意  你得坚持到他们到达\NConcentrate. You gotta keep it up until they land.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.74,1:59:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.50,2:00:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里应该可以\NThis should work.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.92,2:00:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那边和那边都有遮蔽\NGood blinds over there, and there.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.92,2:00:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在附近吗\NThey still close?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.97,2:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,应该越来越近了\NGetting closer, I think.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.99,2:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很难坚持\NThis is tough.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.08,2:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  不用多久了\NI know. I know. Not much longer.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.37,2:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  乌鸦老爹\NOkay, Crow Daddy,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.87,2:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去抓她吧\Ngo get her.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.22,2:01:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来挺放松\NYou look relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.83,2:01:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉放松  是吧  阿布拉\NYou feel relaxed, don't you, Abra?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.56,2:01:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧\NI guess.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.65,2:01:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该这样\NYou should.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.55,2:01:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,放松\NJust relax.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.41,2:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友\NWe're friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.09,2:01:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是朋友\NYou're friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.73,2:01:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.91,2:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只是朋友\NJust friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.04,2:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想带你见更多朋友\NAnd we want to take you to meet more friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.78,2:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好朋友\NGood friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.46,2:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,靠\NWell, shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.99,2:01:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把你说得那么厉害\NThe way they talked you up,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.82,2:01:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为不会这么轻易抓到你呢\NI was thinking it'd be a little harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.18,2:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\NThe fuck?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.02,2:01:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小戏法  只是该死的小戏法\NParlor tricks. Just fuckin' parlor tricks.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.83,2:02:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不  离开那里\NNo! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.67,2:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,离开那里\NGet out of there!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.43,2:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.26,2:02:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.28,2:02:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们活该\NYou deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.52,2:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们所有人都活该\NYou deserve it. All of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.18,2:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.91,2:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.10,2:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.91,2:03:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一个问题问你  亲爱的\NI just got one question for you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.05,2:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想睡吗\NAren't you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.43,2:04:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你想睡了\NYou're sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.04,2:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\NSleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.14,2:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\NSleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.88,2:04:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒  丹叔叔\NWake up! Uncle Dan!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.43,2:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒  醒醒\NWake up! Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.85,2:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.33,2:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的男人\NFucking men.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.51,2:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的男人\NFucking men.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.65,2:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来  比利\NStay back, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.49,2:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,自杀吧\NKill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.62,2:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.78,2:04:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,比利\NBilly!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.73,2:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,少了一个\NThere is one missing.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.01,2:05:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到乌鸦  乌鸦在哪\NI didn't see the Crow. Where is the Crow?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.90,2:05:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  阿布拉\NHello, Abra.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.36,2:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.65,2:05:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,离她远点\NGet away from her.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.62,2:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,退后\NStep back.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.54,2:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  爸爸\NSure thing, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.89,2:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴能见到你\NYou know, I'm glad I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.80,2:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要杀了你  退后\NI'll fucking kill you. Step back.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.61,2:05:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真敢说\NSome brave words.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.41,2:05:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看你们这些凡人威胁神总让我发笑\NAlways tickles me, watching you rubes threaten a god.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.15,2:05:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  你的女儿\NYou know, your little girl,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.26,2:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会成为我们吃过最好的食物\Nshe's maybe the best food we'll ever have.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.91,2:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴能有机会向大厨致意\NI'm so glad I had a chance to compliment the chef.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.51,2:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  你醒了\NGood, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.71,2:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,丹\NDan...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.77,2:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别费劲了\NDon't bother.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.29,2:07:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是怎么了\NWhat's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.25,2:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你被下药了  小姐\NYou've been dosed, missy.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.53,2:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没用过这么大的剂量\NMore than I've ever used before.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.08,2:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能时不时会醒过来\NMight let you wake up here and there,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.52,2:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的灵气睡得很沉\Nbut that steam of yours is fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.18,2:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸\NMy dad...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.68,2:07:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸怎么了\NWhat happened to my dad?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.59,2:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,今天很多好人被杀了\NLot of good people killed today.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.29,2:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很多好人\NLot of good people.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.32,2:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想告诉你会有人付出代价\NI'd love to tell you someone will pay,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.80,2:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,会有某种正义降临为今天的悲剧做主\Nsome kind of justice raining down on the sad events today,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.17,2:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实并非如此\Nbut it don't work like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.16,2:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总是会抓到你的\NWe were always gonna have you.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.16,2:07:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一些人死了\NSome of my people are dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.60,2:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一些人死了\NSome of yours are dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.29,2:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不过结果没变\NOutcome didn't change, though.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.51,2:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想一下\NThink on that a minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.69,2:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,结果没变\NThe outcome didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.17,2:07:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们的死\NSo, their deaths,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.43,2:07:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所有人\Nall of them,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.43,2:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都是白死\Njust a waste.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.70,2:08:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为你的所作所为  小姑娘\NA waste you brought on to us all, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.25,2:08:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.22,2:08:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请听到我的声音\NPlease hear me...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.08,2:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有人听到\NAin't nobody hearing you.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.83,2:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不如冷静下来  享受旅行\NMight as well calm down and enjoy the ride.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.51,2:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我说的\NLike I said,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.80,2:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,结果没变\Noutcome hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:38.24,2:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.19,2:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.93,2:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托  拜托\NOh, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.34,2:08:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.95,2:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.71,2:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.97,2:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,托尼\NTony?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:07.31,2:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,求你帮帮我  托尼\NHelp me, please, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.00,2:09:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.54,2:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好  好\NOkay. Okay. Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.21,2:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  你总是说\NOkay, you always said...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.79,2:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的大脑就像无线电\Nyour brain was like a radio.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.55,2:09:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫的时候没人回应  就不要呼叫了\NNo one's answering when you call, so stop calling.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.46,2:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听就可以\NAnd just listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.50,2:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,丹  丹\NDan. Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.20,2:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\NHelp.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.47,2:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀\N谁\N棒球男孩\N希望你没事\N你的朋友  丹
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.69,2:10:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,丹\NDan.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.92,2:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他给你下药了吗\NDid he drug you?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.57,2:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:25.33,2:10:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我试试别的办法  好吗\NI'm gonna try something, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.42,2:10:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你很虚弱\NBut you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.60,2:10:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他在阻隔你\NHe's blocking you.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.20,2:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎听不见你说话\NI could barely hear you.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:32.53,2:10:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你得相信我  好吗\NYou gotta trust me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:35.80,2:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.21,2:10:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,又醒了吗\NAwake again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.45,2:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可能得在下个休息区给你下药\NMight have to dose you at the next rest stop.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:58.94,2:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪里\NWhere are we going?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.32,2:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你心里很清楚\NYou know where.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.75,2:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,操  我感觉就像宿醉\NFuck, I feel hungover.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.61,2:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你那是好货\NI told you it's good shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.19,2:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好几年没宿醉了  我并不想念这种感觉\NHaven't felt hungover in years. And, you know, I don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:14.37,2:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不\NNot even a little.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.87,2:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,往西走吗\NWest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.72,2:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,远离主路  很明智\NStayin' off the major roads. Smart.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.87,2:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,克朗威尔  纽约\NCrownville. New York.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:30.35,2:11:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.70,2:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是杀了你朋友的人\NI'm the guy that killed your friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.50,2:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你\NIt's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.77,2:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,戏法不错\NNeat trick.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.39,2:11:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,之间没见过这样的\NHaven't seen this one before.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.51,2:11:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想再看一个吗\NWanna see one more?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.30,2:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是对我开枪  萝西应该不会开心\NDon't imagine Rose'll be too happy if you shoot the prize.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.54,2:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,出这些事萝西应该一点都不开心\NI don't suppose Rose will be happy about any of this.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.15,2:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女人要是生气了\NAnd when that woman gets mad...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.82,2:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你知道得够多了\NWell, it seems to me you know enough
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.30,2:12:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,清楚你就不该管这事\Nto know you might wanna sit this one out.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.34,2:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知足\NCount your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.83,2:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,过你自己的生活\NGo on your way.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.84,2:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事这么好笑\NWhat's so funny, friend?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.42,2:12:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是傲慢  真的就是傲慢\NWell, it's just arrogance. It's arrogance, really.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.43,2:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过如果觉得自己可以永生  倒也说得通\NBut it makes sense, if you think you're gonna live forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.96,2:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很显然  你不会想着系安全带\NStands to reason, of course you wouldn't wear your seatbelt.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.96,2:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.52,2:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,丹\NDan?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.30,2:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,丹\NDan?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.99,2:13:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿你感到很痛\NI hope that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.15,2:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,萝西\NRosie...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.37,2:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,非常痛\NA lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.47,2:14:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你个小婊子\NYou little bitch.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.59,2:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你都干了什么\NWhat have you done?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.07,2:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊  小婊子\NAll right, bitch child.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.05,2:14:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.26,2:15:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:52.61,2:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,睡过去了\NDozed off.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.68,2:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  你该睡会儿\NNo, you earned it.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.90,2:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪里\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:00.28,2:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,俄亥俄\NOhio.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.16,2:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪里\NWhere are we going?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.21,2:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多\NColorado.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:05.88,2:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是科罗拉多\NWhy Colorado?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.11,2:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她还会来的\NShe's gonna keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.90,2:16:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道  -不会停下\N- I know. - Always.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.73,2:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只有解决了她才会结束\NThis only ends if we end it,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:17.02,2:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得我们打不过她\Nand I don't think we can beat her.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.58,2:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠我们两个不行\NNot by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:23.47,2:16:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个地方\NThere's a place.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.92,2:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一个对我们这样的人来说很危险的地方\NA place that's dangerous for people like us.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:27.80,2:16:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你说过的那个饥饿的地方吗\NThe place you told me about? The hungry place?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:30.82,2:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错\NYeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.06,2:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那么危险  我们为什么还要去\NIf it's so dangerous, why would we go there?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.50,2:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果对我们来说很危险\NWell, if it's dangerous for people like us,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.92,2:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想对她来说也会很危险\NI expect it's dangerous for people like her.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:40.95,2:16:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可能对她更危险\NMaybe even more so.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:43.63,2:16:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:45.77,2:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她在跟踪我们\NShe's following us, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.65,2:16:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  让她跟着吧\NYeah, good. Let her.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.28,2:16:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸的事我很遗憾\NI'm sorry about your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:02.55,2:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友的事我也很遗憾\NSorry about your friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.56,2:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是我妈妈\NIt's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.33,2:17:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要怎么跟她说\NWhat do I say to her?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.47,2:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NHi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:36.76,2:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\NThank God!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:37.81,2:17:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:38.96,2:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗  你在哪里\NAre you okay? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.61,2:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.84,2:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们安全了  你会告诉她去哪找我们吧\NWhen we're safe, you'll call her and tell her where to find us?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:48.24,2:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:49.47,2:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.45,2:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有多远了  就在山上\NNot too much further. Up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.15,2:18:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,第六章
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.88,2:18:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,遗忘之物
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.40,2:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这么办\NHere's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:03.81,2:20:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你待在车里  一直开着暖气\NYou're gonna stay in the car, keep the heater running.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:07.02,2:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,除非万不得已\NI don't want you spending a minute
Dialogue: 0,2:20:08.22,2:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让你在里面待哪怕一分钟\Ninside there if you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.21,2:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她只能从这里过来\NShe can only come from here.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.08,2:20:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,隔着一公里多你就能看见她\NYou can see her a mile out, easy.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.45,2:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是看见那边山上有灯光\NYou see lights on the mountain over there,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.91,2:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就告诉我  好吗\Nyou blast me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:17.40,2:20:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让你进去  除非她来了\NBut I don't want you going in. Not until she's here.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.79,2:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不和我一起等吗\NYou aren't waiting with me?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:23.35,2:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.31,2:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.26,2:20:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把它弄醒\NI have to wake it up.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.74,2:21:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒\NWakey-wakey.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.83,2:22:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,危险  高压电
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.06,2:24:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.63,2:26:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚有些无聊  托伦斯先生\NSlow night, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:12.69,2:26:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就不会无聊了\NNot for long, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.21,2:26:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢威士忌  对吧\NYou're a whiskey man, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.20,2:26:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,以前大多数时候都喜欢\NI was, most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:28.02,2:26:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,免费赠送\NOn the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:33.25,2:26:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你喜欢的牌子\NThis was your brand.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.40,2:26:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·丹尼尔\NJack Daniel's.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:37.19,2:26:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前在家里看过这酒瓶\NI used to see the bottles in our home.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:39.67,2:26:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在此之前真正的家\NOur real home, before all this.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:43.14,2:26:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有次我闻了一下  感觉象是什么烧着了\NI smelled one once. It smelled like something on fire,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.08,2:26:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我的感觉没错\Nwhich I suppose it was.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:50.15,2:26:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你是把我跟别人搞混了\NI'm afraid you've confused me with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:52.83,2:26:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫劳伊德\NIt's Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.94,2:26:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,劳伊德\NLloyd.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.51,2:26:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  托伦斯先生\NI apologize, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:59.68,2:27:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道大家都去哪里了  但是会热闹起来的\NI don't know where everyone is, but it'll pick up.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:03.67,2:27:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们在哪里\NOh, I know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:05.61,2:27:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得没错\NAnd you're right...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:07.52,2:27:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,会热闹起来的\Nit'll pick up.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:10.88,2:27:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意  托伦斯先生  你似乎\NIf you don't mind my saying, Mr. Torrance, you seem...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.19,2:27:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,被利用了\Nput upon.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:17.36,2:27:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,被利用了\NPut upon?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.21,2:27:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样吗\NAin't that the way.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:21.50,2:27:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,男人过着自己的生活\NMan just living his life,
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.52,2:27:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,努力做好自己的工作\Ntrying to do his work.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.66,2:27:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,结果被利用了\NHe gets put upon.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:27.71,2:27:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,牵扯进别人的麻烦\NPulled into other people's problems.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:29.56,2:27:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我见得太多了  请别介意我这么说\NI see it all the time, if you don't mind my saying.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.25,2:27:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,后来我们住在佛罗里达\NSo we lived in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:38.25,2:27:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\NI'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:39.31,2:27:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我和妈妈\NMom and I.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:41.39,2:27:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我不知道你说的是谁\NI'm afraid I don't know who you mean.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:46.18,2:27:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再也不想看见雪\NWe never wanted to see snow again,
Dialogue: 0,2:27:49.30,2:27:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们住在佛罗里达\Nso we lived in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:51.35,2:27:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,房子很小  但很舒适  我们很幸福\NTiny place, but it was comfortable, and we were happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:54.78,2:27:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也很悲伤\NI mean, we were grieving.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:59.35,2:28:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受到了精神创伤\NWe were traumatized,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.28,2:28:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但同时也有快乐幸福\Nbut there was happiness too.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:06.37,2:28:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她\NShe...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.94,2:28:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她会移开目光\NShe would look away.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:11.00,2:28:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她看着我\NShe'd look at me,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:11.62,2:28:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但一两秒后总会移开目光\Nbut she'd always look away after a second or two.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:15.79,2:28:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,过了段时间我才注意到\NIt took me a while to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:16.98,2:28:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但在眺望酒店之后  她不会直视我的眼睛\NBut after the Overlook, she wouldn't look me in the eyes,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:19.97,2:28:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不会一直看着\Nnot for long.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:22.04,2:28:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直不理解\NCouldn't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:26.04,2:28:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实\NBut it...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.81,2:28:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是你\NIt was you.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:34.49,2:28:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她在我眼中看见你  就不得不移开目光\NShe saw your eyes in me, and she'd have to look away.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:39.57,2:28:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这让她备受折磨\NIt tortured her to have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.29,2:28:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我治好了\NSo, I fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:43.00,2:28:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮她治好了  那是我最后一次用它\NI fixed it for her, and it was the last time I ever used it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:46.30,2:28:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样她就不会再在我眼中看到你\NSo that she wouldn't see you anymore when she looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:52.42,2:28:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她去世的时候我二十岁\NI was 20 when she died.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:54.85,2:28:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我能看出来有人要死了\NAnd back then, I saw when someone was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:58.57,2:29:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看见苍蝇  黑苍蝇\NI saw flies. Black flies.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:00.89,2:29:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我称之为"死蝇"  它们会绕着人脸飞\N"Death flies," I called them, circling people's faces.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:04.76,2:29:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,最后那几周  她满脸...\NAnd in those last weeks, she was covered...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:07.53,2:29:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,满脸都是苍蝇\NHer whole face.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.35,2:29:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎看不见她的眼睛\NI could barely see her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.69,2:29:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着安慰她  但是我几乎没法直视她\NAnd I... I tried to comfort her, but I could hardly look at her.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:17.54,2:29:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她看出来了\NAnd she saw that.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:21.69,2:29:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她就躺在那里奄奄一息\NShe just lay there dying,
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.92,2:29:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而她的儿子都没法直视她\Nwith her son who couldn't look at her.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:31.87,2:29:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,或许喝点烈的来忘掉那种不快\NMaybe something warm to push away such unpleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:35.43,2:29:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想听听吗  她是你妻子\NDon't you wanna hear about it? She was your wife.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.62,2:29:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可能把我当成了别人\NI think you've mistaken me for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:41.74,2:29:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只是个酒保  -是吗\N- I'm just a bartender. - Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:45.06,2:29:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只是酒保劳伊德  在眺望酒店倒倒酒\NJust Lloyd the bartender, pouring joy at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:48.24,2:29:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你想喝什么我都给你  托伦斯先生\NI'll pour whatever you like, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:52.45,2:29:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\NOh, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:55.48,2:29:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这杯酒代价必然不菲\NThis drink will cost an awful lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:57.85,2:29:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的钱在这里没用\NYour money is no good here.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:59.87,2:30:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,免费赠送\NOrders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:01.55,2:30:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它的代价不在于金钱\NIt'll cost more than money.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.64,2:30:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它会毁掉我的八年努力\NIt'll cost me eight years.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.11,2:30:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的八年  谁知道我未来还有几年\NEight behind me, and who knows how many in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:08.65,2:30:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你的信用没问题  托伦斯先生\NYour credit is fine, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:18.34,2:30:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,君唤一壶酒\NMan takes a drink,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:21.33,2:30:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,千杯入愁肠\Nthe drink takes a drink,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.92,2:30:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,酒销人已亡\Nand then the drink takes a man.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:26.87,2:30:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样吗  爸\NAin't it so, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:32.71,2:30:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,药\NMedicine.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:35.62,2:30:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它就是药\NMedicine is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:38.51,2:30:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的灵丹妙药\NBona fide cure-all.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.65,2:30:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抑郁  压力  悔恨  失败  一扫而光\NDepression, stress, remorse, failure, wipes it all away.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:47.25,2:30:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,思想就是一块黑板\NThe mind is a blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:49.99,2:30:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而这个\NAnd this
Dialogue: 0,2:30:51.94,2:30:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是黑板擦\Nis the eraser.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:58.61,2:31:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,男人努力工作\NA man tries.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:00.94,2:31:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,养家糊口\NHe provides.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.24,2:31:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但他周围都是张大的嘴\NBut he's surrounded by mouths.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:05.57,2:31:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭  尖叫  哭喊  唠叨\Nthat eat, and scream, and cry, and nag.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:08.77,2:31:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他只为自己求一样东西\NSo, he asks for one thing, just one thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:12.33,2:31:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,暖暖身子\NTo warm him up...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:14.09,2:31:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,逃离被那些嘴支配的痛苦\Nto take the sting out of those days of the mouths,
Dialogue: 0,2:31:16.99,2:31:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,它们不停地吃  吃掉他制造的一切\Neating, and eating, and eating everything he makes,
Dialogue: 0,2:31:19.79,2:31:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他拥有的一切\Neverything he has.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:22.15,2:31:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有家庭\NAnd a family.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:23.97,2:31:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子和孩子\NA wife, a kid.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:27.45,2:31:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那些嘴吃掉时间\NThose mouths eat time.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:29.96,2:31:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,吃掉你在人间的时日\NThey eat your days on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:32.86,2:31:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它们狼吞虎咽\NThey just gobble them up.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:36.04,2:31:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,足以让一个男人崩溃\NIt's enough to make a man sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:39.63,2:31:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而这个\NAnd this...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:41.75,2:31:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是良药\Nis the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:45.81,2:31:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  小子\NSo, tell me, pup,
Dialogue: 0,2:31:48.81,2:31:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你要吃药吗\Nare you gonna take your medicine?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:54.29,2:31:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要\NI'm not.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:59.34,2:32:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思  我很抱歉\NLook at that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:00.72,2:32:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我这老家伙笨手笨脚的  请原谅  托伦斯先生\NClumsy old me, Mr. Torrance. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:05.30,2:32:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让我帮你擦干净吧\NLet's get you cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:25.13,2:32:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,上头很担心\NManagement is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:27.29,2:32:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,担心\NConcerned?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:30.80,2:32:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她对你做的事太糟糕了\NIt's horrible what she's done to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:33.38,2:32:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把你卷进她的麻烦\NPulled you into her mess.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:37.48,2:32:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明人会怎么做呢\NA smart man?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:40.16,2:32:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会让她自己解决\NHe'd let her handle it.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:43.02,2:32:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让事情按本该的样子发展\NLet things unfold as they're meant to.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:46.47,2:32:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,凭什么要你为他买单呢  医生\NWhy should you pay her tab, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:50.64,2:32:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么呢\NAnd for what?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:52.56,2:32:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了这个惹来所有麻烦的小姑娘吗\NFor this little girl who started all this trouble?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:56.61,2:32:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那上头想让我怎么做\NWhat would management have me do about that?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:59.72,2:33:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不做\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:01.99,2:33:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世间最容易的事情  孩子\NEasiest thing in the world to do, son.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:04.92,2:33:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带进来\NJust bring her inside.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:07.13,2:33:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后\NAnd then, well,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:09.56,2:33:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,接受自己无法改变的事情\Nyou accept the things you cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:13.88,2:33:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,丹\NDan!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.03,2:33:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她来了\NShe's here.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.17,2:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:50.07,2:33:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方病了\NThis place is sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:52.64,2:33:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我奶奶一样\NSick like my momo was sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:55.18,2:33:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她得了癌症\NIt's cancer,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:56.91,2:33:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但这地方比那还糟\Nonly worse.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:06.43,2:34:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在做什么\NWhat do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:07.77,2:34:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去  她会来找我们\NWe head inside. She'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:59.89,2:36:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快瞧瞧\NWell, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:04.09,2:36:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好啊\NHi there.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.83,2:36:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦开始  你就赶快跑\NWhen this starts, run.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:09.05,2:36:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  你跑吧  亲爱的\NYes, you run, dear.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:11.90,2:36:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我会找到你\NAnd then I will find you
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.31,2:36:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你尖叫许多年再死去\Nand you will scream for years until you die.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:20.35,2:36:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,倒要瞧瞧谁是尖叫的那一个\NWe'll see who does the screaming.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:22.90,2:36:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我们走着瞧\NOh, we'll see indeed.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:24.63,2:36:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她说的没错\NShe's right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:26.67,2:36:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该感到害怕\NYou should be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:29.48,2:36:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy is that?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:31.80,2:36:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不知道你身处何处\NBecause you don't know where you're standing.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:34.56,2:36:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  帅哥  你是哪位\NI'm sorry, who are you, handsome?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:40.96,2:36:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你是杀了我的乌鸦  对吧\NYou're the one who killed my Crow, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:45.74,2:36:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,开始\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:47.98,2:37:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真聪明\NClever.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:50.34,2:37:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了不少改进是吧\NYou've made some improvements, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:53.68,2:37:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我上次侵入你的脑子之后\NSince the last time I was in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:56.36,2:37:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎知道不是我们侵入了你的脑子\NHow do you know we're not in yours?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:12.72,2:38:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪呢  小家伙\NWhere are you, pup?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:34.89,2:38:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你将死在这里\NYou're gonna die here.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.30,2:38:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真敢说  亲爱的\NBrave words, dear.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:40.69,2:38:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是那么想的吗\NIs that what you really think?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:43.00,2:38:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你能伤到我\NYou're gonna hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:45.66,2:38:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:53.48,2:38:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我想起了我自己\NYou know, you remind me of myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:58.17,2:38:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在看明白了\NI can really see it now.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:00.64,2:39:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你内心深藏着黑暗  亲爱的\NYou've got a darkness in you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:03.21,2:39:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你我之间唯一的区别  就是时间\NI think the only difference between you and me is time.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:16.22,2:39:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不知道\NYou don't know yet...
Dialogue: 0,2:39:18.55,2:39:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为了拥有更多的时间\Nwhat you'd do...
Dialogue: 0,2:39:20.72,2:39:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,人都会做些什么\Nfor more time.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:23.61,2:39:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我跟你保证  亲爱的  你会感到惊讶的\NBut I promise you, dear, oh, you'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:32.50,2:39:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,疼痛净化灵气\NPain purifies steam.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:35.53,2:39:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,恐惧亦然  请你理解\NFear, too, so, you understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:59.03,2:40:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我年轻时和你一模一样\NI was just like you when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:01.88,2:40:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常特别\NI was special
Dialogue: 0,2:40:04.38,2:40:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也孤身一人\Nand alone.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:05.86,2:40:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但我遇到了给予我归属和使命的人\NBut I met someone who gave me the gift of purpose, of community.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:08.95,2:40:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果事情不是发展至此\NAnd I might have given you such a gift
Dialogue: 0,2:40:11.06,2:40:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来也可能给予你同样的馈赠\Nif things would have gone differently.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:16.73,2:40:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吗\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:18.93,2:40:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你很目中无人  是吧\NDefiant, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:21.94,2:40:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和我真像\NSo much like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:23.49,2:40:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脑子如此...\NYour mind is so...
Dialogue: 0,2:40:28.96,2:40:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的脑子  对吗\NThis isn't your mind, is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:33.67,2:40:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本不是你\NThis isn't you at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:37.58,2:40:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是个诱饵\NYou're just the bait.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:43.49,2:40:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:47.77,2:40:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\NRun.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:51.31,2:40:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么会没发现你\NHow the hell did we miss you?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:56.79,2:40:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你我本该多年前就相识\NYou and I should have met years ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:02.82,2:41:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\NDanny.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:04.96,2:41:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的名字  对吧\NThat's your name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:08.90,2:41:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当凡人变老  灵气会发生一些变化\NWell, something happens to the steam when you rubes get older.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:12.53,2:41:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,会被污染\NIt gets polluted.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:14.71,2:41:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,变得肮脏\NDirty.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:16.33,2:41:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\NYou know that.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:18.67,2:41:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看见你浑身的污秽\NI see the grease all over you.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:21.67,2:41:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的闪灵和以前不太一样了\NYou don't shine quite the same.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.47,2:41:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,成长糟蹋了你的闪灵\NGrowing up spoils that, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:29.12,2:41:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的  帅哥\NSeriously, handsome,
Dialogue: 0,2:41:31.44,2:41:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么多年都躲在哪里\Nwhere have you been hiding?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:36.81,2:41:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你开个条件\NI can make you an offer.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:40.21,2:41:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一个我绝少开的条件\NAn offer I rarely make.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:41.95,2:41:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  我真期待呢\NOh, yeah? I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:44.49,2:41:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如此天赋异禀的男孩\NSuch a gifted boy
Dialogue: 0,2:41:46.51,2:41:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,长久以来深藏不露\Nhiding his light under a bushel for so long.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:50.34,2:41:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以活得很久  也可以活得很好\NYou could live a long, long time. Live well, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:54.87,2:41:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情放纵  无需承担后果\NIndulge yourself, no consequences,
Dialogue: 0,2:41:59.26,2:42:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会宿醉\Nno hangovers.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:02.55,2:42:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吃得好  长生不老\NEat well, live long.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:05.30,2:42:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩你一个了  你肯定很孤单\NYou must be lonely, being the last one.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:08.25,2:42:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界只剩你一个\NI mean, the last one in the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:10.48,2:42:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我可不是最后一个  差得远呢\NSweetie, I'm not the last. Far from it.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:14.24,2:42:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我只不过是最漂亮的一个\NI'm just the prettiest.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:16.05,2:42:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想必你已经知道我的答复了\NI assume you know my answer.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:19.74,2:42:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太可惜了\NPity.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:20.99,2:42:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们还打不打了\NSo, are we doing this or not?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.18,2:42:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\NOh, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:46.26,2:42:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\NLook at that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:49.26,2:42:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎伤到了你的股动脉\NI seem to have nicked your femoral artery there.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.52,2:42:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你会失血过多而死  是吗\NWhy, you're gonna bleed to death, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:01.82,2:43:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老天  你脾气还真是倔\NMy, my, what a temper you have.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:04.17,2:43:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,火气不小\NSo much fire.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:05.89,2:43:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真是浪费\NSuch a waste!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:07.67,2:43:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是浪费\NOr maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:16.21,2:43:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\NOh, damn.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:18.56,2:43:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,即便在你这个岁数\NEven at your age...
Dialogue: 0,2:43:21.03,2:43:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还是如此美味\Nit's so good.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:27.89,2:43:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你尝起来就像威士忌\NYou taste like whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:35.14,2:43:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\NDanny!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:37.38,2:43:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小丹尼\NDanny boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:38.82,2:43:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,红朗姆
Dialogue: 0,2:43:40.55,2:43:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如此深重的恐惧\NOh, so much terror.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:42.50,2:43:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的一生都如此吗\NAll your life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:46.58,2:43:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太美味了\NDelicious.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:55.11,2:43:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别伤害我\NDon't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:58.15,2:43:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\NOh, damn.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:03.90,2:44:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么...不只有你一个\NWhat are... You're not alone in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:07.54,2:44:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你还藏了什么\NWhat are you hiding, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:11.19,2:44:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是什么\NWhat's in those?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:12.90,2:44:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,特别的东西  是吧\NSomething special, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:15.28,2:44:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才不特别  他们饿坏了\NThey're not special. They're starving.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:26.76,2:44:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:27.27,2:44:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:28.36,2:44:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:45:07.26,2:45:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  丹尼\NHello, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:11.09,2:45:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来和我们一起玩\NCome and play with us...
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.68,2:45:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\Nforever...
Dialogue: 0,2:45:17.36,2:45:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\Nand ever...
Dialogue: 0,2:45:20.21,2:45:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,永永远远\Nand ever.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:56.23,2:45:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,丹叔叔\NUncle Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:58.58,2:46:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,丹叔叔  搞定了吗\NUncle Dan, is it done?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:01.29,2:46:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她死了吗\NIs she dead?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:24.65,2:46:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,派对很棒吧\NGreat party, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:26.96,2:46:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,2:46:32.13,2:46:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,2:46:49.69,2:46:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,2:46:57.55,2:46:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra!
Dialogue: 0,2:47:17.60,2:47:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\NTry it.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:22.18,2:47:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这呢\NThere you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:23.62,2:47:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,阿布拉\NAbra.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:25.88,2:47:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你很不乖哦\NYou've been very, very bad.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:28.50,2:47:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是丹叔叔\NYou're not Uncle Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:30.79,2:47:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是一个面具  一张假的面孔\NYou're a mask. A false face.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:35.08,2:47:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我能是谁\NWho else would I be?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:36.58,2:47:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这家酒店\NYou're the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:38.18,2:47:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但他仍然存在\NBut he's still in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:39.70,2:47:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就摘掉面具吧\NMask is off, then.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:46.03,2:47:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么笑\NWhy are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:48.09,2:47:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不知道你身处何处\NBecause you don't know where you're standing.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:51.60,2:47:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这些走廊了如指掌  孩子\NI know these halls like my own face, child.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:54.23,2:47:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说你身处的这具躯体\NI mean the body you're standing in.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:56.42,2:47:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴起的这幅面孔\NThe face you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:58.37,2:48:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是丹·托伦斯  而你并不了解他\NThat's Dan Torrance, and you don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:00.37,2:48:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,丹·托伦斯\NDan Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:02.23,2:48:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,丹·托伦斯来到这里做的第一件事\NDan Torrance made one stop as soon as he got here.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:06.81,2:48:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是去了锅炉房\NTo the boiler room.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:34.08,2:48:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\NThere you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:36.77,2:48:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是让你跑吗\NYou were supposed to run.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:38.51,2:48:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想扔下你\NI didn't wanna leave you.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:43.10,2:48:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在我本该在的地方\NI'm exactly where I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:46.85,2:48:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法抵抗他们太久  阿布拉  你得赶快离开\NI can't hold it off for much longer. Abra, you need to run.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:49.60,2:48:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:50.63,2:48:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我哪也不去\NI'm not going anywhere without you.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:52.66,2:48:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把我们身后的门关上  不是吗\NI have to close the door behind us, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:55.91,2:48:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跑  快跑\NRun! Run!
Dialogue: 0,2:51:11.85,2:51:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  丹叔叔\NCome on, Uncle Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:13.60,2:51:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快出来\NGet out of there.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:16.23,2:51:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:29.06,2:51:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,火势扩散地很快\NThe fire spread fast,
Dialogue: 0,2:51:31.52,2:51:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,毁掉了酒店\Ndestroying the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:33.44,2:51:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,净化了它\NPurifying it.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:36.40,2:51:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎能听到它的...\NI could almost hear it...
Dialogue: 0,2:51:38.50,2:51:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,尖叫\Nscreaming.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:40.81,2:51:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我能听到它在死去\NI could hear it dying.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:43.54,2:51:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而内心深处  我知道...\NAnd deep inside, I knew...
Dialogue: 0,2:51:49.06,2:51:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你没事\NI knew you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:52.35,2:51:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我让你身处险境\NI'm sorry I put you in danger.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:55.32,2:51:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是唯一的办法\NIt was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:57.70,2:51:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:00.10,2:52:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为她说的是真的吗\NDo you think she was right
Dialogue: 0,2:52:03.35,2:52:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是最后一个\Nwhen she said she wasn't the last one?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:06.63,2:52:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个饥肠辘辘的世界\NThe world's a hungry place.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:08.91,2:52:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,非常黑暗\NA dark place.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:11.59,2:52:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也许像他们那样的人还有更多\NMaybe there's more of them
Dialogue: 0,2:52:12.74,2:52:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,或是比他们更可怕的东西\Nor things like them or worse,
Dialogue: 0,2:52:13.82,2:52:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但也有更多像你一样的人\Nbut there are more people like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:17.83,2:52:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,挺身而出的人\NPeople who stand.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:23.14,2:52:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次见到你时\NI told you when I first met you,
Dialogue: 0,2:52:24.79,2:52:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就告诉你应该藏起来\NI told you that you should hide.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:29.13,2:52:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,应该低调行事\NThat you should keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:32.28,2:52:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,掩藏你的闪灵能力\NKeep your shine out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:36.15,2:52:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我错了\NBut I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:40.84,2:52:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,展现你的闪灵吧  阿布拉·斯通\NShine on, Abra Stone.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:45.61,2:52:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情展现\NYou shine on.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:50.54,2:52:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,晚饭好了\NDinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:52:54.85,2:52:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你和谁说话呢\NWho are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:58.70,2:52:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没谁\NNo one.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:07.95,2:53:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我说谎了\NThat's not true.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:13.43,2:53:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我在和丹说话\NI was talking to Dan.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:22.70,2:53:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们死后仍然存在\NWe go on after.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:25.68,2:53:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,仍然存在\NWe go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:27.61,2:53:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他没事\NAnd he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:29.93,2:53:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸也是\NSo is Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:32.50,2:53:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的没事\NHe really is.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:37.86,2:53:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,2:53:50.66,2:53:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃饭吗  宝贝\NYou coming, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:54.69,2:53:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,马上\NIn a minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:54:56.43,2:55:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,? Midnight with the stars and you ?\NMidnight, The Stars and You - Ray Noble and His Orchestra
Dialogue: 0,2:55:03.42,2:55:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,? Midnight and a rendezvous ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:10.21,2:55:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,? Your eyes held a message tender ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:15.82,2:55:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,? Saying "I surrender all my love to you" ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:24.60,2:55:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,? Midnight brought us sweet romance ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:31.56,2:55:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,? I know all my whole life through ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:38.77,2:55:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,? I'll be remembering you ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:41.89,2:55:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,? Whatever else I do ?
Dialogue: 0,2:55:45.71,2:55:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,? Midnight with the stars and you ?

